%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20%26quot%3Binternational%20needs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20includes%20%2413.1%20billion%20for%20equipment%20and%20other%20military%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20replenishing%20the%20United%20States'%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-increasing-production-of-155mm-artillery-shells-2023-1%5C%22%3Ediminished%20weapons%20stockpiles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20asks%20Congress%20for%20%247.3%20billion%20in%20economic%2C%20humanitarian%2C%20and%20security%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20countries%20impacted%20by%20Russia's%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%2C%20supplemental%20request%20would%20cover%20the%20projected%20cost%20of%20aiding%20Ukraine%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20a%20senior%20administration%20official%20said%20on%20a%20call%20with%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20longer%20this%20war%20is%20going%20to%20go%20on%20or%20how%20much%20more%20assistance%20we%20might%20need%20to%20support%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20won't%20be%20bashful%20about%20going%20back%20to%20Congress%20beyond%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20next%20year%20if%20we%20feel%20like%20we%20need%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20is%20on%20top%20of%20the%20%246%20billion%20that%20the%20White%20House%20requested%20earlier%20this%20year%20as%20part%20of%20the%202024%20budget.%20Since%20the%20invasion%2C%20the%20US%20has%20provided%20Ukraine%20with%20more%20than%20%24100%20billion%20in%20security%20and%20financial%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20comes%20alongside%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20request%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirefighters-pay-raise-biden-budget-request-hawaii-wildfire-2023-8%5C%22%3Esupplemental%20funding%20toward%20disaster%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20borde