businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Ffederal-reserve-balance-sheet-inflation-rate-hike-monetary-policy-crash-2022-11%5C%22%3EFed's%20quantitative%20tightening%3C%2Fa%3E%20via%20its%20monthly%20balance%20sheet%20reductions%20could%20put%20a%20dent%20in%20stock%20prices%20and%20other%20risk%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20June%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Ffederal-reserve-balance-sheet-inflation-rate-hike-monetary-policy-crash-2022-11%5C%22%3Ethe%20Fed%20has%20reduced%20its%20balance%20sheet%20by%20%24900%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%247.6%20trillion%2C%20and%20it%20would%20have%20been%20even%20more%20if%20the%20Fed%20wasn't%20forced%20to%20inject%20%24400%20billion%20of%20liquidity%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-fed-hiking-interest-rates-after-silicon-valley-bank-collapse-2023-3%5C%22%3Econtain%20the%20regional%20banking%20crisis%20in%20March.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Fed%20reduces%20its%20balance%20sheet%20by%20letting%20treasury%20and%20mortgage%20bonds%20mature%20(and%20then%20not%20reinvesting%20the%20proceeds)%2C%20it%20is%20taking%20liquidity%20out%20of%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLiquidity%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20the%20financial%20markets...%20Risk%20assets%20love%20liquidity.%20Continued%20draining%20of%20liquidity%20presents%20a%20risk%20for%20equities%20and%20credit%2C%26quot%3B%20Ned%20Davis%20Research%20chief%20global%20macro%20strategist%20Joseph%20Kalish%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20has%20been%20reducing%20its%20balance%20sheet%20by%20about%20%2480%20billion%20per%20month%2C%20and%20stocks%20tend%20to%20perform%20well%20when%20the%20exact%20opposite%20happens%2C%20according%20to%20NDR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20analysis%20shows%20that%20when%20the%204-week%20change%20of%20reserves%20has%20increased%20by%20more%20than%20%2462%20billion%2C%20stock%20returns%20have%20exploded%20at%20a%2031%25%20annual%20rate%20since%20March%202009%20when%20the%20Fed%20began%20ramping%20up%20QE%20and%20shifted%20to%20an%20ample%20reserves%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalish%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConversely%2C%20when%20reserves%20have%20been%20declining%20by%20more%20than%20%2438%20billion%20over%20the%20past%20four%20weeks%2C%20stocks%20have%20struggled%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalish%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20stocks%20could%20still%20come%20under%20pressure%20even%20if%20the%20Fed%20pauses%20its%20interest%20rate%20hiking%20cycle%20for%20good%20later%20this%20year%2C%20as%20the%20central%20bank%20has%20shown%20no%20indication%20of%20stopping%20its%20balance%20sheet%20reduction%20program.%20And%20its%20balance%20sheet%20reduction%20policy%20can%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20not%20only%20on%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20but%20also%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reduction%20in%20securities%20shrinks%20bank%20reserves%2C%20which%20reduces%20banks'%20cash%20and%20limits%20their%20ability%20to%20make%20loans%20and%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalish%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20combined%20with%20aggressive%20interest%20rate%20hikes%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20helps%20explain%20the%20tightening%20in%20credit%20conditions%20and%20the%20reduced%20willingness%20of%20banks%20to%20loan%20out%20money.%20But%20whether%20the%20Fed's%20ongoing%20tightening%20policies%20can%20knock%20down%20this%20year's%20stock%20market%20rally%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-risk-outlook-fed-balance-sheet-liquidity-drain-rates-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691697668000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60394378d920880018592435%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-risk-outlook-fed-balance-sheet-liquidity-drain-rates-2023-8%22%