usinessinsider.com%2Fteachers-caught-students-cheating-chatgpt-survey-shows-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20the%20chatbot%20to%20cheat%20and%20plagiarize%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20their%20assignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20professors%20at%20colleges%20across%20the%20US%20and%20beyond%20are%20trying%20out%20ways%20to%20%26quot%3BChatGPT-proof%26quot%3B%20their%20assignments%2C%20as%20concerns%20grow%20that%20students%20may%20be%20missing%20out%20on%20learning%20by%20using%20AI%20cut%20corners%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-ai-detection-tool-shut-down-over-inaccuracy-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etools%20that%20detect%20AI-generated%20text%20have%20been%20found%20to%20be%20prone%20to%20errors.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBonnie%20MacKellar%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20professor%20at%20St.%20Johns%20University%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said%20that%20she%20is%20making%20students%20in%20her%20intro%20courses%20take%20paper%20exams%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einstead%20of%20digital%20ones%20and%20having%20them%20handwrite%20their%20code.%20Paper%20exams%20will%20be%20a%20bigger%20portion%20of%20her%20students'%20grades%20this%20fall%2C%20she%20said%2C%20compared%20to%20previous%20semesters.%20In%20turn%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estudents%20will%20be%20disincentivized%20to%20outsource%20their%20logical%20thinking%20to%20AI%2C%20which%20she%20said%20could%20stunt%20their%20learning%20and%20leave%20them%20unprepared%20for%20more%20advanced%20computer%20science%20classes%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hear%20colleagues%20in%20humanities%20courses%20saying%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20It's%20back%20to%20the%20blue%20books%2C%26quot%3B%20MacKellar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20professors%20seek%20to%20curb%20AI%20cheating%20by%20reframing%20assignment%20questions%20so%20students%20are%20required%20to%20%26quot%3Bshow%20their%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20William%20Hart-Davidson%2C%20an%20associate%20dean%20at%20Michigan%20State%20University%20who%20leads%20AI%20workshops%20for%20faculty%20members%2C%20told%20Insider%20over%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssignment%20questions%2C%20Hart-Davidson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bshould%20include%20a%20request%20for%20students%20to%20be%20explicit%20and%20reflective%20about%20the%20moves%20they%20are%20making.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20just%20want%20them%20to%20reproduce%20a%20fact%20or%20a%20rote%20response%2C%20but%20to%20learn%20to%20account%20for%20their%20reasoning%20in%20a%20deliberate%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20ChatGPT%20can%20easily%20answer%20a%20straight-forward%20question%20like%20%26quot%3BTell%20me%20in%20three%20sentences%20what%20is%20the%20Krebs%20cycle%20in%20chemistry%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20this%2C%20Hart-Davidson%20told%20Insider%20that%20teachers%20should%20reframe%20the%20question%20to%20something%20like%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Brevise%20an%20existing%20passage%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20the%20Krebs%20cycle%2C%20which%20would%20require%20students%20to%20point%20out%20errors%2C%20identify%20writing%20for%20clarity%20and%20accuracy%2C%20and%20explain%20how%20the%20writing%20could%20be%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20way%2C%20students%20are%20forced%20to%20think%20through%20their%20answers%2C%20rather%20than%20regurgitate%20what%20a%20chatbot%20tells%20them%2C%20which%20Hart-Davidson%20said%20could%20help%20improve%20their%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20professors%20suggest%20students%20show%20their%20work%20by%20including%20their%20editing%20history%20and%20drafts%20along%20with%20their%20completed%20assignments.%20A%20document%20that%20logs%20all%20the%20typos%20corrected%20and%20the%20sentences%20rephrased%20in%20an%20essay%20can%20prove%20that%20a%20human%20wrote%20it%2C%20Dave%20Sayers%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Jyv%C3%A4skyl%C3%A4%20in%20Finland%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeshighereducation.com%2Fcampus%2Fsimple-hack-chatgptproof-assignments-using-google-drive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20for%20the%20Times%20Higher%20Education%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20education%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20guide%20from%20Butler%20University%20in%20Indianapolis%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flibguides.butler.edu%2Fai-in-the-classroom%2Fchatbot-proof-assignments%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20chatbot-proof%20assignments%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20teachers%20could%20eliminate%20the%20essay%2C%20issue%20impromptu%20oral%20exams%2C%20and%20foster%20classroom%20discussions%20around%20how%20to%20best%20use%20the%20chatbot's%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20to%20school%20assignments%20come%20as%20teachers%20grapple%20with%20how%20to%20best%20integrate%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20into%20their%20classrooms.%20While%20some%20professors%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwharton-mba-professor-requires-students-to-use-chatgpt-ai-cheating-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erequire%20their%20students%20to%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20generate%20project%20ideas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-schools-colleges-ban-plagiarism-misinformation-education-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20schools%20have%20outright%20banned%20the%20usage%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20avoid%20cases%20of%20academic%20dishonesty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20controversy%2C%20some%20teachers%20are%20using%20AI%20chatbots%20themselves%20to%20streamline%20their%20workflows.%20Shannon%20Ahern%2C%20a%20high%20school%20math%20and