0the%20hall%20from%20the%20brewery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20spoke%2C%20Edel%20stretched%20two%20thin%2C%20dirt-dusted%20fingers%20into%20his%20half-full%20beer%20glass%20to%20pinch%20a%20fungus%20gnat%20out%20of%20the%20golden%20liquid.%20The%20bug%20must%20have%20made%20itself%20at%20home%20in%20the%20live%20plants%20rooted%20in%20a%20strip%20of%20dirt%20and%20rock%20running%20down%20the%20center%20of%20the%20long%20wooden%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22john%20edel%20thin%20man%20with%20white%20beard%20round%20glasses%20blue%20shirt%20sits%20in%20a%20bar%20behind%20a%20plant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ce9e9df5d4870019e2668c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEdel%20sits%20in%20the%20taproom%20of%20Whiner%20Beer%20Co.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20McFall-Johnsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20garden%20centerpieces%20sprouted%20from%20other%20tables%20in%20the%20dim%20light%20of%20the%20large%20concrete%20and%20brick%20chamber.%20Patrons%20talked%2C%20gestured%2C%20and%20laughed%20through%20gaps%20in%20the%20broad%20leaves%2C%20giving%20the%20space%20a%20buzz%20as%20lively%20as%20its%20greenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20mostly%20regard%20us%20with%20curiosity%2C%20like%2C%20'What%20is%20this%20strange%20place%20and%20what%20do%20you%20do%20in%20there%3F'%26quot%3B%20Edel%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20try%20to%20make%20it%20as%20inviting%20and%20open%20as%20possible%20for%20people%20to%20come%20in%20and%20learn%20what%20we%20do%20and%20hopefully%20learn%20about%20some%20aspect%20of%20food%20production%20or%20sustainability%20or%20loop%20closing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuilt%20for%20pork%20and%20beef%20but%20perfect%20for%20indoor%20farms%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rows%20of%20green%20plants%20with%20yellow%20flowers%20growing%20on%20shelves%20beneath%20led%20gro