0businesses%20in%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20kind%20of%20has%20that%20mentality%20of%20using%20each%20other's%20garbage%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIn%20the%20'cool%20ship%2C'%20bacteria%20from%20the%20farms%20help%20brew%20beer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETucked%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20brewery%2C%20hidden%20behind%20a%20plywood%20board%2C%20is%20a%20small%20room%20wrapped%20in%20tubing%20that%20once%20piped%20ammonia%20for%20refrigeration.%20A%20giant%20vat%20fills%20the%20space.%20It%20was%20covered%20with%20a%20wooden%20board%20on%20this%20visit%2C%20but%20it's%20often%20full%20of%20beer%20or%2C%20sometimes%2C%20kombucha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22flat%20wooden%20surface%20fills%20a%20room%20with%20rows%20of%20pipes%20wrapping%20around%20the%20perimeter%20and%20curved%20wooden%20slats%20from%20barrels%20hanging%20on%20the%20ceiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ceebb8f5d4870019e26d37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20the%20%26quot%3Bcool%20ship%2C%26quot%3B%20bacteria%20from%20the%20farms%20gets%20coughed%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20brewing%20beer.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20McFall-Johnsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20put%20in%20a%20duct%20that%20pulls%20air%20from%20above%20one%20of%20the%20outdoor%20farms%20and%20basically%20coughs%20it%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20hot%20beer%20that's%20come%20out%20of%20the%20brewing%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Edel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20will%20%26quot%3Bbasically%20infect%20the%20beer%26quot%3B%20with%20bacteria%20that%20help%20it%20ferment%2C%20he%20added.%20Bowed%20wood%20from%20barrels%20hangs%20on%20the%20ceiling%20above%20to%20attract%20bonus%20bacteria%2C%20which%20live%20in%20the%20wood%20and%20later%20fall%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20beer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20call%20this%20room%20%26quot%3Bthe%20cool%20ship.%2