p%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20for%20The%20Plant's%20digester%20was%20that%20it%20would%20consume%2032%20tons%20of%20food%20waste%20each%20day%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20liquid%20digestate%2C%20some%20compostlike%20solids%2C%20and%20biogas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biogas%20would%20power%20boilers%20throughout%20the%20building.%20The%20solids%20would%20enrich%20soil.%20The%20Plant's%20laboratories%20could%20extract%20growth%20stimulants%20from%20the%20liquid%20for%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20digester%20is%20key%20to%20The%20Plant's%20larger%20mission%2C%20Edel%20said%3A%20%26quot%3Bcoming%20up%20with%20ways%20to%20take%20the%20waste%20that%20surrounds%20us%20all%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20food%20and%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22line%20of%20stainless%20steel%20doors%20with%20bathroom%20signs%20on%20them%20down%20a%20hallway%20with%20plants%20in%20bright%20light%20above%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ceec9620f1cf0019cb5f10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOld%20smokehouses%20have%20been%20converted%20into%20bathrooms%20throughout%20the%20building.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20McFall-Johnsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20costs%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20more%20than%20expected.%20It%20would%20take%20another%20%242%20million%20to%20get%20the%20digester%20up%20and%20running%2C%20according%20to%20Edel.%20For%20now%2C%20that's%20not%20financially%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20work%20but%20only%20marginally%2C%20and%20we%20need%20it%20to%20really%20sing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20the%20laboratories%20on%20the%20top%20floor%20are%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20make%20the%20digester%20profitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20ultimate%20circle%20of%20food%20production%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20lit%20chandelier%20hangs%20at%20the%20top%20of%20a%20dark%20stairwell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ce9e9c20f1cf0019cb57fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20the%20top%20of%20a%20stairwell%20leading%20to%20the%20top%20floor%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20just%20the%20most%20absurd%20chandelier%20I%20could%20find%2C%26quot%3B%20Edel%20said.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20McFall-Johnsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELeonard%20Lerer%20and%20three%20employees%20of%20his%20company%2C%20Back%20of%20the%20Yards%20Algae%20Sciences%2C%20sit%20among%20the%20whirring%20machines%20and%20tubes%20of%20floating%20algae%20in%20the%20laboratory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20primary%20mission%20is%20finding%20ways%20to%20use%20algae%20and%20fungi%20as%20replacements%20for%20artificial%20food%20additives%3A%20colorants%2C%20flavors%2C%20protein%20powders%2C%20and%20even%20plant%20stimulants%20for%20indoor%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22four%20men%20sit%20around%20a%20long%20table%20with%20beer%20and%20plates%20in%20a%20laboratory%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ce9e9ff5d4870019e26690%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeonard%20Lerer%2C%20second%20from%20the%20left%2C%20runs%20Back%20of%20the%20Yards%20Algae%20Sciences%20from%20the%20laboratories%20in%20The%20Plant.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20McFall-Johnsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20side%2C%20Back%20of%20the%20Yards%20Algae%20Sciences%20has%20taken%20on%20the%20ambitious%20project%20of%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20extract%20valuable%20molecules%20from%20waste%20in%20the%20anaerobic%20digester.%20The%20innovators%20believe%20they%20can%20pull%20antioxidants%20or%20vanilla%2C%20for%20example%2C%20from%20the%20digesting%20food%20waste%20and%20sell%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20can%20extract%20valuable%20molecules%2C%20Edel%20said%2C%20that%20will%20be%20the%20promise%20he%20needs%20to%20invest%20the%20%242%20million%20to%20finish%20the%20anaerobic%20digester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20labs%20are%20working%20on%20a%20pilot%20experiment%20with%20a%20mini%20digester%20to%20test%20their%20idea.%20Edel%20expects%20the%20pilot%20to%20start%20running%20in%20future%C2%A0months%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22yellow%20counter%20with%20glass%20tubes%20full%20of%20dark%20algae%20running%20along%20the%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d28d8711d6ad0019ed48a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlgae%20sits%20in%20tubes%20at%20the%20laboratory.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20McFall-Johnsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELerer's%20hope%20is%20that%20the%20laboratory's%20work%2C%20and%20implementation%20of%20these%20techniques%20in%20farms%20at%20The%20Plant%2C%20can%20help%20make%20vertical%20farming%20more%20sustainable%20and%20profitable.%20If%20it%20worked%20at%20scale%2C%20indoor%20vertical%20farming%20would%20use%20less%20land%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20water%20than%20traditional%20crop%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20ultimate%20circular%20vision%20for%20The%20Plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20the%20waste%20from%20vertical%20farming%20or%20food%20waste%2C%20put%20it%20in%20an%20anaerobic%20digester%2C%20generate%20energy%20%E2%80%94%20gas%2C%20or%20turn%20that%20into%20electricity.%20Use%20the%20digestive%20that%20comes%20off%20to%20feed%20algae.%20The%20algae%20make%20a%20biostimulant%2C%20which%20you%20give%20back%20to%20the%20plants%2C%20which%20allows%20it%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20Lerer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222019%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22turtle%20in%20clear%20shallow%20water%20with%20pebbles%20along%20the%20bottom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ceeccbf5d4870019e26d98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C