falling%20from%20the%20second-floor%20balcony%20of%20the%20main%20hostel%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwapnadip%20Kundu%20(18)%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bagula%20in%20Nadia%20district%2C%20was%20an%20undergraduate%20student%20of%20Bengali%20(honours).%20He%20allegedly%20fell%20from%20a%20hostel%20building%20around%2011.45%20pm%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20received%20multiple%20injuries%20and%20died%20at%204.30%20am%20during%20treatment%20at%20the%20KPC%20Medical%20College%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Chancellor%20of%20the%20university%2C%20visited%20the%20hostel%20and%20assured%20Swapnadip's%20father%20of%20stern%20action%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20his%20son's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClasses%20for%20the%20first%20year%20began%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20back%2C%20as%20another%20student%20of%20that%20year%20alleged%20that%20ragging%20by%20a%20few%20seniors%20was%20behind%20his%20friend's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitial%20probe%20revealed%20that%20the%20student%20was%20bullied%20allegedly%20by%20some%20senior%20boarders%20of%20the%20hostel%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said%20adding%20that%20he%20called%20up%20his%20mother%20at%20around%209%20PM%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20expressed%20his%20fear%20%26quot%3Babout%20something%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20phone%20got%20switched%20off%20later.%20We%20are%20looking%20into%20his%20call%20list%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20he%20spoke%20to%20anyone%20else%20after%20that%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20examined%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20his%20roommates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20post-mortem%20examination%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20that%20the%20boy%20was%20in%20mental%20distress%20after%20seniors%20started%20terming%20him%20gay.%20There%20are%20witnesses%20when%20he%20started%20showing%20discomfort%20regarding%20this.%20He%20called%20up%20his%20mother%20at%20least%20four%20times%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20also%20deactivated%20his%20Facebook%20account%20in%20the%20evening%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJU%20Registrar%20Snehamanju%20Basu%20said%20in%20a%20communique%20to%20the%20Jadavpur%20police%20station%20said%20the%20said%20student%20was%20found%20on%20the%20road%20in%20front%20of%20the%20main%20hostel%20within%20the%20campus%20in%20unconscious%20and%20wounded%20condition%20%26quot%3Bat%2011%20pm%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdespite%20every%20step%20taken%20for%20immediate%20and%20best%20possible%20treatment%20for%20him%2C%20he%20died%20at%206%20am%20today.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20allegation%20of%20Swapnodip's%20father%20that%20his%20son%20is%20a%20victim%20of%20ragging%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said%20that%20they%20were%20talking%20to%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20hostel%20and%20also%20the%20students%20who%20have%20recently%20started%20staying%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20another%20first-year%20student%20of%20Jadavpur%20University%20alleged%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20that%20ragging%20by%20%E2%80%9Ca%20few%20seniors%E2%80%9D%20was%20behind%20the%20death%20of%20his%20friend%20Swapnodeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20name%20is%20Arpan%20Majhi.%20I%20am%20a%20first-year%20student%20at%20Jadavpur%20University.%20My%20family%20is%20economically%20backward%20and%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20Asansol.%20Naturally%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20a%20hostel%20during%20admission.%20Spending%20two%20to%20three%20nights%20at%20the%20hostel%20was%20quite%20tormenting%20to%20me%20and%20because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20have%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20mess%20despite%20facing%20great%20difficulty%2C%20even%20if%20I%20have%20to%20take%20a%20loan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20that%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20ragging%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20senior%20boarders%20at%20the%20hostel%2C%20Majhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20heard%20many%20stories%20about%20the%20main%20hostel.%20Stories%20of%20them%20helping%20flood%20victims%2C%20standing%20by%20the%20side%20of%20helpless%20people%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20I%20believe%20most%20of%20the%20seniors%20in%20the%20main%20hostel%20carry%20this%20fighting%20tradition.%20But%20for%20a%20few%20of%20them%2C%20I%20lost%20my%20classmate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JU%20chapter%20of%20the%20All%20Bengal%20University%20Teachers'%20Association%20(ABUTA)%20alleged%20that%20the%20varsity%20authorities%20did%20not%20take%20any%20steps%20to%20stop%20ragging%20despite%20knowing%20about%20this%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadavpur%20University%20Teachers%20Association%20(JUTA)%20Secretary%20Partha%20Pratim%20Roy%20called%20for%20keeping%20new%20students%20in%20a%20separate%20hostel%20as%20per%20UGC%20rules%20and%20immediately%20driving%20out%20former%20students%20who%20had%20been%20living%20in%20the%20hostel%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20demand%20exemplary%20punishment%20for%20those%20responsible%20for%20his%20fate%2C%26quot%3B%20Roy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20varsity's%20Arts%20Faculty%20Students%20Union%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20a%20full%20probe%20into%20the%20incident%20and%20punishment%20for%20the%20guilty.%20We%20stand%20by%20the%20family%20of%20the%20victim.%20We%20also%20want%20that%20allegations%20of%20physical%20torture%20of%20freshers%20are%20not%20raised%20again.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20evening%2C%20Governor%20Bose%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20hostel%20and%20spoke%20to%20the%20boarders%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20to%20the%20father%20of%20the%20victim%20and%20assured%20him%20of%20%26quot%3Bstern%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20those%20who%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20death.