th%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20as%20part%20of%20a%20special%20series%20to%20mark%20the%2076th%20Independence%20Day%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%20while%20there%20is%20disturbance%20in%20Manipur%2C%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20is%20criticising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20or%20the%20Home%20Minister%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20is%20saying%20this%20is%20happening%20because%20of%20the%20Central%20government.%20Earlier%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20happened%2C%20the%20blame%20would%20have%20come%20to%20Delhi.%20Now%2C%20people%20know%20this%20is%20our%20conflict%2C%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20in%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20had%20moved%20a%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20in%20parliament%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20conflict%20is%20on%20since%20May%20and%20you%20will%20see%20that%20politicians%20from%20the%20mainland%20are%20criticising%20Modi%2C%20but%20nobody%20from%20Manipur%20is%20blaming%20Narendra%20Modi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20motion%20got%20defeated%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20parliament%20today%20by%20a%20comfortable%20margin.%20Their%20strategy%20to%20pin%20down%20the%20government%20and%20compel%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20speak%20on%20Manipur%20also%20crashed%2C%20with%20PM%20Modi%20launching%20on%20a%20two-hour-plus%20speech%20that%20ripped%20through%20the%20Opposition%20and%20blamed%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%202015%20after%20decades%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20said%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20northeast%20has%20changed%20considerably%20since%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20it%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20been%20brought%20about%20by%20better%20connecti