20Bank%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20launched%20the%20new%20linkage%20in%20association%20with%20his%20Singaporean%20counterpart%20Ravi%20Menon%2C%20who%20is%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Monetary%20Authority%20of%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20third%20monetary%20policy%20review%2C%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%20the%20RBI%20was%20planning%20to%20use%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20UPI%20payments%20and%20also%20to%20deploy%20near-field%20communication%20(NFC)%20technology%20to%20be%20used%20in%20offline%20payments%20in%20UPI-Lite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20enhanced%20the%20transaction%20limit%20for%20small-value%20digital%20payments%20to%20Rs%20500%20from%20Rs%20200%20on%20UPI%20Lite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20UPI%20linkages%20with%20more%20countries%2C%20the%20deputy%20governor%20T%20Rabi%20Shankar%20told%20reporters%20that%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20integration%20has%20already%20been%20done%20with%20Singapore.%20And%20recently%20we%20signed%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20UAE's%20payment%20system%20Integrated%20Payment%20Platform%20(IPP)%20to%20link%20UPI%20with%20their%20payment%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress%20and%20it%20will%20happen%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20and%20discussions%20are%20underway%20with%20a%20few%20other%20countries%20also%20for%20linking%20their%20payment%20systems%20with%20ours%2C%20including%20some%20advanced%20economies%20which%20have%20evinced%20interest%20in%20linking%20to%20UPI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Das%20chipped%20in%20saying%20%26quot%3BUPI%20has%20now%20become%20internationally%20recognised.%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20it%20myself%2C%20but%20it%20is%20recognised%20very%20widely%2C%20and%20that%20it%20is%20perhaps%20the%20most%20efficient%20and%20advanced%20payment%20system%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20recent%20G20%20finance%20ministers%20and%20governors%20meeting%2C%20UPI%20was%20widely%20recognised.%20So%20this%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%20We%20are%20already%20in%20discussion%20with%20a%20few%20other%20countries%20and%20it%20will%20happen%20soon.%26quot%3B%20To%20a%20question%20from%20a%20Japanese%20journalist%20whether%20some%20officials%20from%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20economy%20has%20contacted%20RBI%20for%20UPI%20linkage%2C%20Shankar%20answered%20in%20the%20affirmative%20saying%20a%20Japanese%20minister%20has%20contacted%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20happy%20that%20a%20country%20like%20Japan%20which%20is%20an%20advanced%20economy%2C%20is%20showing%20interest%20in%20the%20UPI.%20Currently%2C%20it%20is%20only%20at%20an%20intention%20stage%20as%20the%20contact%20was%20mostly%20exploratory%20level.%20NPCI%20is%20talking%20to%20the%20relevant%20Japanese%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20deputy%20governor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAK%20Goel%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Banks'%20Association%20(IBA)%20said%20more%20user-friendly%20measures%20for%20UPI%20by%20way%20of%20conversational%20payments%20in%20UPI%20and%20further%20promoting%20the%20UPI-Lite%20by%20facilitating%20offline%20transactions%20using%20near%20field%20communication%20are%20expected%20to%20widen%20the%20coverage%20of%20UPI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691688000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Ftijempgs_upi-payments-generic_625x300_12_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fmore-nations-including-japan-few-from-west-interested-in-upi-rbi-4287572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reserve%20Bank%20on%20Thursday%20said%20the%20internationalization%20of%20the%20unified%20payments%20interface%20(UPI)%20system%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress%20as%20it%20works%20towards%20linking%20it%20with%20m