20in%20which%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20victory%20was%20predetermined%20because%20of%20the%20sheer%20numbers%20it%20commands%20in%20both%20the%20Houses%2C%20eventually%20became%20yet%20another%20opportunity%20for%20him%20to%20take%20down%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20even%20as%20he%20skirted%20the%20Manipur%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20had%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20move%20the%20motion%20only%20to%20get%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20burning%20Manipur%20issue%20in%20parliament.%20They%20had%20argued%20that%20since%20Modi%20had%20remained%20largely%20absent%20in%20parliament%2C%20there%20was%20no%20other%20way%20to%20get%20him%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20time%20was%20devoted%20to%20taking%20down%20allegations%20and%20criticisms%20that%20Gandhi%20had%20made%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%20(August%209)%20that%20for%20many%20observers%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20may%20come%20across%20as%20a%20rejoinder%20to%20the%20Wayanad%20MP.%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3Ehad%20attacked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Modi%20government%20primarily%20on%20three%20counts.%20He%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cahankar%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(arrogance)%20to%20not%20notice%20the%20sufferings%20of%20people%20of%20Manipur%2C%20even%20as%20he%20attacked%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20supposed%20cronyism.%20Gandhi%20then%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20that%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20neglect%20in%20Manipur%20and%20apparent%20failure%20to%20douse%20communal%20flames%20in%20Haryana%20amounted%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20its%20leaders%20%E2%80%9Cmurdering%20Mother%20India%E2%80%9D%20and%20its%20diverse%20voices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%2C%20in%20his%20response%2C%20touched%20upon%20the%20problems%20in%20Manipur%20for%20barely%20ten%20minutes%20in%20his%20over%20two-hour-long%20speech.%20He%20urged%20the%20political%20class%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20Manipur%20conflict%20together%2C%20assured%20that%20the%20wrongdoers%20will%20be%20severely%20punished%2C%20and%20claimed%20that%20his%20government%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20find%20a%20resolution%20to%20the%20unfortunate%20sectarian%20conflict%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELapsing%20into%20whataboutery%2C%20Modi%20recalled%20multiple%20incidents%20where%20the%20Congress%20allegedly%20fuelled%20conflicts%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20states%2C%20bungled%20economic%20growth%2C%20and%20promoted%20sectarian%20politics%2C%20even%20as%20he%20spoke%20about%20how%20India%20and%20its%20institutions%20are%20shining%20under%20his%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3EIn%20a%202-Hour-Long%20Speech%20in%20Parliament%2C%20PM%20Modi%20Spoke%20for%20Less%20Than%2010%20Minutes%20on%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20even%20as%20he%20spoke%20about%20his%20achievements%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20contrasted%20them%20with%20the%20Congress%20governments.%20He%20trained%20his%20guns%20primarily%20at%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%2C%20the%2026%20party%20opposition%20front%2C%20even%20while%20speaking%20about%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%2C%20like%20all%20the%20BJP%20MPs%20and%20ministers%2C%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20call%20INDIA%20as%20%E2%80%9CI.dot%2C%20N.dot%2C%20D.dot%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20mostly%20as%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cghamandiya%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20claim%20the%20front%20was%20power-hungry%20and%20arrogant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EYeh%20ghamandiya%20gathbandhan%20parivaarvaad%20ki%20rajniti%20ka%20sabse%20bada%20pratibimb%20hai%20%3C%2Fi%3E(This%20%3Cem%3Eghamandiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20alliance%20is%20the%20biggest%20reflection%20of%20dynasty%20politics)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EAvishwaas%20and%20ghamand%20inke%20ragon%20mein%20bas%20gaya%20hai%3C%2Fi%3E%20(Disbelief%20and%20arrogance%20are%20now%20running%20in%20their%20veins)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20about%20the%20Congress%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20only%20believed%20in%20perpetuating%20%E2%80%9Cnegativity%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%20that%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20of%20the%20country%20supported%20him%20and%20his%20government%2C%20the%20Congress%20can%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20reality%20as%20it%20did%20not%20trust%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ability%20and%20grit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20then%20went%20on%20to%20talk%20about%20some%20of%20the%20contradictions%20of%20INDIA.%20He%20pointed%20out%20how%20in%20states%20like%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Kerala%2C%20two%20INDIA%20constituents%20Congress%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20had%20historically%20opposed%20each%20other.%20He%20added%20that%20socialists%20who%20build%20their%20respective%20parties%20by%20opposing%20the%20Congress%20have%20now%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20latter.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20Dravidian%20party%2C%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%2C%20and%20some%20other%20INDIA%20constituents%20did%20not%20think%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20a%20part%20of%20India%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-speech-ideology-india-alliance%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Speech%3A%20An%20Alliance%20Leader%20Steering%20the%20Ideological%20Beliefs%20of%20INDIA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20signal%20that%20the%20INDIA%20was%20a%20coming%20together%20of%20opportunistic%20parties%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%20his%20response%20to%20the%20no-trust%20motion%20only%20betrayed%20the%20seriousness%20with%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20opposition%20front%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constant%20attempt%20to%20run%20down%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20by%20pointing%20out%20its%20internal%20contradictions%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20which%20have%20already%20been%20discussed%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties%20in%20their%20last%20two%20meetings%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20isn%E2%80%99t%20casual%20about%20the%20opposition%20front%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20prospects%2C%20despite%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20frequent%20claims%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20is%20well%20on%20its%20way%20to%20form%20a%20government%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20displayed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20the%20core%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20must%20be%20derailed%2C%20attacked%2C%20and%20even%20demonised%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20The%20Congress%20will%20be%20locked%20in%20a%20direct%20contest%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20around%20180-odd%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20and%20is%20hopeful%20of%20improving%20its%20performance%20with%20the%20support%20of%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speeches%20in%20the%20parliament%20have%20increasingly%20become%20an%20opportunity%20for%20him%20to%20attack%20the%20Congress%2C%20even%20as%20he%20has%20skirted%20the%20debates%20in%20focus.%20He%20avoided%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajya-sabha-pm-modi-speech-adani%5C%22%3Eanswering%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20US-based%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20may%20have%20committed%20financial%20fraud%20even%20when%20he%20spoke%20last%20in%20both%20the%20Houses%20during%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20debate%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20then%20was%20demanding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-adani-lok-sabha-speech%5C%22%3Ea%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20US-based%20financial%20firm.%20On%20every%20such%20occasion%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20made%20it%20a%20pattern%20to%20skirt%20the%20issues%20in%20focus%2C%20and%20instead%20make%20%3Ci%3Ead%20hominem%20%3C%2Fi%3Eattacks%20on%20the%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20shouting%20%E2%80%9CModani%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20last%20two%20speeches%20in%20parliament%2C%20they%20were%20shouting%20%E2%80%9CManipur%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%20as%20Modi%20spoke%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20opposition%20eventually%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20House%20in%20protest%20after%20Modi%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20touched%20upon%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20nearly%20two%20hours%20into%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20singular%20focus%20on%20the%20Congress%20during%20his%20speech%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20surprising%2C%20given%20the%20pattern%20he%20has%20shown%20during%20his%20previous%20speeches.%20However%2C%20what%20surely%20came%20across%20as%20a%20little%20puzzling%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20especially%20lash%20out%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20each%20of%20his%20allegations%20he%20made%20a%20day%20ago.%C2%A0%20The%20recently%20reinstated%20Congress%20leader%20may%20have%20indeed%20touched%20a%20raw%20nerve.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691687626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10224035%2Fimage-1212.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpm-modis-speech-shifting-focus-from-manipu