ow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20cheetahs%20in%20Kuno%20died%20due%20to%20maggot%20infections%20and%20authorities%20have%20been%20subjecting%20all%20the%20remaining%20cheetahs%20%E2%80%93%20including%20free-ranging%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20to%20health%20checks.%20The%20move%20came%20after%20two%20cheetahs%20died%20due%20to%20maggot%20infestations%20on%20July%2011%20and%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20radio%20collars%20caused%20abrasion%20and%20the%20moisture%20that%20accumulated%20under%20the%20collars%20due%20to%20the%20monsoon%20humidity%20resulted%20in%20septicaemia%20or%20an%20infection%20of%20the%20blood.%20The%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(NTCA)%2C%20however%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fauthorities-say-recent-cheetah-deaths-due-to-natural-causes-mp-chief-wildlife-warden-transferred%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20this%20is%20untrue%20and%20that%20all%20cheetahs%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20August%207%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20reason%20to%20disbelieve%E2%80%9D%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20the%20efforts%20it%20was%20taking%20to%20stop%20cheetah%20deaths%20in%20Kuno%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1053987%2Fcheetah-deaths-no-reason-to-disbelieve-centres-efforts-to-save-them-says-supreme-court%5C%22%3Eper%20reports.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESearch%20on%20for%20Nirva%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20authorities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fninth-cheetah-dies-in-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20Dhatri%2C%20the%20other%20free-ranging%20cheetah%20in%20Kuno%2C%20dead%20on%20August%202%2C%20their%20efforts%20have%20been%20focused%20on%20capturing%20Nirva%2C%20the%20last%20cheetah%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20for%20a%20health%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20the%20evening%20of%20August%2010%2C%20ground%20teams%20have%20still%20not%20been%20able%20to%20track%20down%20Nirva%2C%20said%20a%20source%20in%20the%20state%20forest%20department%20who%20is%20involved%20with%20Project%20Cheetah.%20The%20source%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%20as%20a%20gag%20order%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fproject-cheetah-media-gag-order%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20issued%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20officials%20associated%20with%20the%20Project%20to%20not%20talk%20to%20the%20media%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20obtain%20a%20direct%20sighting%20of%20Nirva%2C%20but%20they%20have%20found%20%E2%80%9Cclues%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20indirect%20signs%20such%20as%20pugmarks%20and%20scat%20%E2%80%93%20in%20some%20spots%20and%20are%20searching%20those%20areas%2C%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirva%E2%80%99s%20radio%20collar%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fauthorities-yet-to-capture-last-two-free-ranging-cheetahs-in-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3Erun%20into%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkuno-officials-fall-back-on-traditional-methods-to-track-two-cheetahs-one-radio-collar-silent-8865778%2F%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20working%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20monitoring%20teams%20on%20ground%20to%20locate%20her.%20Nirva%2C%20like%20Dhatri%20(later%20found%20dead%20in%20the%20wild%20on%20August%202)%2C%20is%20also%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20shy%E2%80%9D%2C%20sources%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fauthorities-yet-to-capture-last-two-free-ranging-cheetahs-in-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E.%20This%20makes%20it%20a%20challenge%20to%20get%20close%20enough%20to%20dart%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Fbhopal%2Ffinding-nirva-madhya-pradeshs-kuno-officers-seek-chopper%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20plans%20may%20be%20on%20to%20use%20a%20helicopter%20to%20locate%20the%20missing%20cheetah.%20However%2C%20the%20ground%20team%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20one%20yet%20and%20it%20may%20help%20if%20the%20authorities%20can%20provide%20one%20for%20the%20search%20operation%2C%20the%20source%20on%20ground%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20drones%20are%20being%20used%20to%20search%20the%20landscape%20for%20Nirva%2C%20the%20source%20cited%20above%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECheetah%20deaths%20not%20%E2%80%98low%E2%80%99%2C%20says%20SC%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20said%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20reason%20to%20disbelieve%E2%80%9D%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20the%20efforts%20it%20was%20taking%20to%20stop%20cheetah%20deaths%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fnumber-of-cheetah-deaths-at-kuno-national-park-not-low-says-supreme-court-8880696%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Ci%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2020%20African%20cheetahs%20brought%20into%20Kuno%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20six%20adults%20have%20died.%20Three%20of%20the%20four%20cubs%20born%20to%20one%20of%20the%20female%20cheetahs%20succumbed%20to%20heat%20stroke%2C%20said%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20Choubey%2C%20in%20parliament%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcheetahs-in-kuno-national-park-died-from-traumatic-shock-and-heat-strokes-according-to-india-s-environment-ministry-101689878559589.html%5C%22%3Erecently%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20comprising%20Ju