%20final%20mode%20of%20preparation.%20The%20team%20recently%20ended%20the%20ODI%20series%20against%20West%20Indies%20as%20winners%2C%20despite%20regular%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ex-India%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20featuring%20in%20the%20fional%20two%20games.%20It%20looked%20like%20the%20Indian%20team%20management%20was%20preparing%20for%20a%20contingency%20plan.%20Now%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20said%20that%20nobody%20is%20assured%20of%20a%20place%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20is%20an%20automatic%20(selection)%2C%20even%20I%20am%20not.%20We%20have%20this%20thing%20where%20nobody%20is%20guaranteed%20a%20spot.%20We%20cannot%20say%20that%20'you%20are%20there%20after%20all'%20or%20things%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20some%20players%20know%20that%20they%20are%20going%20to%20play%20but%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time%2C%20playing%20three%20ODIs%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20was%20a%20good%20opportunity%20to%20look%20at%20a%20few%20guys.%20In%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20again%2C%20we%20will%20face%20good%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Asia%20Cup%20will%20take%20place%20from%20August%2030%20with%20India%20facing%20Pakistan%20on%20Sepetmeber%202.%20He%20also%20opened%20up%20on%20India's%20injury%20concerns.%20%26quot%3BShreyas%20and%20KL%20are%20coming%20off%20not%20playing%20anything%20for%20four%20months%2C%20big%20injuries%2C%20surgeries%20rather.%20Both%20had%20surgeries.%20I%20know%2C%20I%20had%20to%20undergo%20surgery%20once%20and%20how%20it%20feels%20afterwards%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20tough.%20We%20have%20to%20see%2C%20how%20they%20respond%2C%20what%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20selection%20(meeting)%20will%20be%20there%20in%20a%20few%20days%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20good%20debate%20about%20what%20we%20can%20do.%20But%20honestly%20nobody%20is%20an%20automatic%20choice%20%E2%80%93%20they%20all%20have%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20spot%20%E2%80%93%20everyone%20has%20to%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20top%20spot%20or%20a%20bottom%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20names%20there.%20We%20will%20see%20what%20is%20right%20combination%20for%20us%20to%20go%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20but%20before%20we%20have%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20India%20skipper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20said%20he%20wants%20some%20of%20the%20Indian%20players%20to%20bat%20under%20pressure%20to%20get%20accustomed%20in%20the%20longer%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20see%2C%20we%20want%20to%20win%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20that%20we%20need%20answers%20of.%20But%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20I%20want%20to%20see%20some%20of%20the%20guys%20batting%20under%20pressure%20against%20quality%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20want%20to%20see%20those%20things%2C%20so%20we%20will%20wait%20and%20see%20what%20happens%2C%20but%20it%20is%20always%20nice%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20names%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20one%20or%20two%20names.%20I%20hope%20they%20are%20fit%20in%20time%20%E2%80%93%20firstly%20that%20is%20the%20most%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Rahul%20and%20Iyer)%20have%20been%20at%20the%20NCA%20for%20the%20last%20four%20months%2C%20working%20really%20hard%20and%20it%20looks%20quite%20positive%20so%20we%20will%20keep%20our%20fingers%20crossed%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691678160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fj7ppne