ours%2C%20but%20we%20could%20not%20see%20justice%20for%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gogoi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20referred%20to%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20long%20speech%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday%2C%20which%20he%20said%20gave%20detailed%20information%20about%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20and%20the%20steps%20the%20centre%20has%20been%20taking%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20had%20also%20tore%20into%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%2C%20asserting%20that%20he%20has%20been%20working%20hard%20on%20bringing%20peace%20and%20has%20been%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20closely%20since%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20early%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20recalled%20how%20PM%20Modi%20dialled%20him%20at%204%20am%20and%206.30%20am%20on%20two%20consecutive%20days%20when%20reports%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20came.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20rejected%20the%20opposition's%20call%20for%20imposition%20of%20President's%20rule%20in%20BJP-ruled%20Manipur%20under%20Article%20356%20of%20the%20Constitution%20as%20playing%20politics%20over%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%221crkoarg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F1crkoarg_manipur-violence_625x300_16_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(opposition)%20keep%20saying%20why%20we%20didn't%20apply%20(Article)%20356%3F%20(Article)%20356%20is%20applied%20when%20during%20turmoil%20the%20state%20government%20doesn't%20cooperate.%20We%20changed%20the%20DGP%2C%20the%20state%20accepted%20the%20centre's%20decision.%20We%20changed%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20the%20state%20accepted%20the%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20opposition's%20query%20why%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20not%20been%20replaced%2C%20