2C%20multiple%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20hearing%20the%20screams%20of%20the%20girl%20and%20her%20mother's%20cries%2C%20people%20came%20out%20of%20their%20houses%20and%20rushed%20to%20help%20her.%20A%20few%20men%20tried%20to%20scare%20away%20the%20cows%20by%20throwing%20stones%20and%20making%20sounds.%20However%2C%20the%20cows%20were%20relentless%20in%20their%20attack%20and%20continued%20to%20assault%20the%20girl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20it%20seemed%20that%20the%20cows%20were%20abandoning%20the%20scene%2C%20but%20they%20came%20back%20to%20attack%20the%20girl.%20The%20cows%20fled%20the%20spot%20only%20when%20a%20local%20with%20a%20stick%20tried%20to%20chase%20them%20away.%20The%20girl%20was%20then%20rescued%20and%20was%20seen%20struggling%20to%20stand%20up.%20She%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20to%20be%20treated%20for%20her%20injuries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cows%20reportedly%20belong%20to%20residents%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20However%2C%20no%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20yet%20as%20the%20family%20is%20reluctant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691676360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fleh6oepg_chennai-cow-attack_625x300_10_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-terrifying-video-chennai-schoolgirl-returning-home-brutally-attacked-by-cow-4287308%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20cows%20suddenly%20turned%20back%20and%20charged%20at%20the%20girl%2C%20lifting%20her%20with%20its%20horns%20and%20throwing%20her%20on%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A120%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-terrifying-video-chennai-schoolgirl-returning-home-brutally-attacked-by-cow-4287308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-terrifying-video-chennai-schoolgirl-returni