gh%20The%20Story%20of%20My%20Brother%2C%20Gurnaib%20Singh%20Gill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10182950%2FGurnaib-Singh-Gill.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dear%20and%20eldest%20brother%20S.%20Gurnaib%20Singh%20Gill%20(85)%20passed%20away%20on%20July%2030%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Faridkot%20after%20a%20brief%20battle%20with%20prostate%20cancer.%20His%20life%20story%20covers%20many%20shifts%20in%20the%20contemporary%20economic%2C%20social%20and%20cultural%20history%20of%20Punjab%2C%20especially%20its%20rural%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20a%20family%20of%20five%20brothers%20and%20five%20sisters.%20As%20the%20eldest%20son%2C%20Bai%20Gurnaib%20became%20acutely%20conscious%20of%20his%20responsibilities%20to%20look%20after%20our%20grandparents%2C%20parents%20and%20his%20younger%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20at%20a%20relatively%20young%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20us%20(brothers%20and%20sisters)%20has%20stories%20to%20tell%20of%20the%20protective%20role%20he%20played.%20He%20took%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20our%20education.%20I%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20his%20special%20affection%20as%20I%20was%20his%20youngest%20brother%20for%20nearly%2013%20years%2C%20until%20a%20younger%20brother%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20my%20mentor%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20but%20especially%20in%20encouraging%20me%20to%20be%20physically%20fit.%20I%20now%20recall%20with%20astonishment%20that%20at%20the%20age%20of%20eight%2C%20I%20used%20to%20run%20two%20miles%20nearly%20every%20day%20to%20prove%20to%20him%20that%20I%20was%20worthy%20of%20his%20affection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20he%20wanted%20me%20to%20study%2C%20he%20would%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20farming%20work.%20He%20feared%20that%20if%20I%20acquired%20any%20farming%20skills%2C%20they%20might%20lead%20me%20to%20get%20interested%20in%20farming.%20Ironic%20as%20it%20may%20be%2C%20he%20later%20became%20the%20chief%20and%20authentic%20source%20of%20my%20primary-level%20knowledge%20about%20many%20aspects%20of%20farming%20when%20I%20started%20doing%20academic%20research%20in%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20research%20work%20was%20a%20dissertation%20on%20farm%20size%20and%20productivity%20in%20Haryana%20for%20my%20MA%20honours%20in%20economics.%20While%20my%20teacher%2C%20the%20late%20Prof%20G.S.%20Bhalla%2C%20was%20the%20academic%20supervisor%2C%20Bai%20Gurnaib%20was%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20the%20economics%20of%20different%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20father%20looked%20upon%20Bai%20Gurnaib%20%E2%80%93%20his%20eldest%20son%20%E2%80%93%20as%20his%20chief%20companion%20in%20managing%20our%20ancestral%20land.%20As%20our%20family%20had%20land%20in%20two%20different%20villages%2C%20our%20father%20deputed%20him%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20entire%20farming%20operations%20in%20one%20of%20the%20villages%20at%20the%20age%20of%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20Punjab%2C%20it%20would%20certainly%20seem%20unthinkable%20for%20such%20a%20young%20man%20to%20assume%20the%20role%20of%20head%20of%20agricultural%20operations%20in%20a%20village%20that%20is%20not%20one%E2%80%99s%20native%20village%2C%20it%20was%20not%20a%20common%20thing%20even%20in%20the%20late%201950s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERural%20life%20has%20many%20charms%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20full%20of%20jealousies%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20conflicts%20that%20vary%20from%20being%20very%20petty%20to%20life-threatening.%20Bai%20Gurnaib%20faced%20many%20challenges%2C%20including%20ones%20which%20were%20life-threatening%2C%20because%20of%20jealousies%20from%20other%20landowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fthe-need-for-land-leasing-reforms-in-punjabs-agricultural-sector%5C%22%3EThe%20Need%20for%20Land%20Leasing%20Reforms%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Agricultural%20Sector%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manner%20he%20devised%20to%20build%20alliances%20in%20the%20new%20village%20is%20illustrative%20of%20the%20caste%20and%20class%20dynamics%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20rural%20society.%20Knowing%20very%20well%20that%20he%20could%20not%20expect%20friendship%20from%20the%20landowners%2C%20Bai%20Gurnaib%20built%20bonds%20of%20strong%20friendship%20with%20landless%20farmers.%20I%20recall%20agricultural%20labourers%20who%20were%20not%20only%20his%20employees%20but%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20the%20first-hand%20experience%20of%20seeing%20those%20Jat%20Sikh-Mazhabi%20Sikh%20relations%20which%20many%20writers%20on%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20rural%20society%20describe%20only%20in%20confrontational%20terms%2C%20but%20are%20much%20more%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20and%20cultural%20modes%20of%20Bai%20Gurnaib%E2%80%99s%20friendships%20with%20his%20Mazhabi%20Sikh%20workers%20displayed%20strong%20signs%20of%20equality%2C%20including%20sometimes%20eating%20and%20drinking%20together%20despite%20economic%20inequality%20between%20him%20and%20the%20agricultural%20workers.%20His%20experience%20had%20a%20formative%20influence%20on%20me%20in%20shaping%20my%20understanding%20of%20caste-class%20dynamics%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20rural%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20relationship%20with%20animals%2C%20especially%20with%20his%20pair%20of%20bullocks%20in%20the%20pre-tractorisation%20phase%20of%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%2C%20had%20many%20dimensions%20of%20close%20human-animal%20relations.%20The%20animal%20power-replacing%20mechanisation%2C%20symbolised%20by%20the%20tractorisation%20phase%2C%20has%20put%20an%20end%20to%20those%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20pre-tractorisation%20phase%2C%20our%20father%20bought%20a%20pair%20of%20Nagori%20bullocks%20from%20the%20famous%20Nagore%20cattle%20market%20in%20Rajasthan.%20The%20pair%20were%20expensive%20and%20attracted%20attention%20from%20surrounding%20villages.%20It%20led%20to%20a%20stream%20of%20farmers%20coming%20to%20our%20house%20to%20see%20these%20new%20entrants%20in%20the%20village%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBai%20Gurnaib%20looked%20after%20his%20pair%20of%20bullocks%20with%20great%20devotion%20and%20a%20deep%20emotional%20bond%20developed%20between%20him%20and%20the%20pair.%20The%20cattle%20would%20respond%20actively%20to%20his%20commands%20in%20a%20way%20one%20would%20normally%20expect%20from%20human%20beings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20spent%20their%20whole%20life%20at%20our%20farm%2C%20and%20their%20death%20at%20a%20ripe%20old%20age%20saw%20a%20period%20of%20deep%20mourning%20for%20all%20family%20members%20%E2%80%93%20but%20especially%20for%20Bai%20Gurnaib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20observations%20Gurnaib%20shared%20with%20me%20about%20the%20organic%20phase%20of%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20and%20the%20industrial-chemical%20phase%20later%20have%20stayed%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20me%20that%20when%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%20started%20being%20used%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fgreen-revolution%5C%22%3EGreen%20Revolution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20confused%20the%20farm%20birds%20so%20much%20that%20they%20mistook%20particles%20of%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%20as%20seeds%20and%20died%20in%20large%20numbers%20after%20consuming%20those%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FAgriculture_in_India_tractor_farming_Punjab_preparing_field_for_a_wheat_crop_without_burning_previous_crop_stalk-1024x678.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FAgriculture_in_India_tractor_farming_Punjab_preparing_field_for_a_wheat_crop_without_burning_previous_crop_stalk-1024x678.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FAgriculture_in_India_tractor_farming_Punjab_preparing_field_for_a_wheat_crop_without_burning_previous_crop_stalk-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FAgriculture_in_India_tractor_farming_Punjab_preparing_field_for_a_wheat_crop_without_burning_previous_crop_stalk-768x509.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FAgriculture_in_India_tractor_farming_Punjab_preparing_field_for_a_wheat_crop_without_burning_previous_crop_stalk.jpg%201280w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-77816%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22556%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPunjab%20led%20the%20Green%20Revolution%20in%20India%20and%20drove%20economic%20growth%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%201960s%20and%2070s.%20Photo%3A%20CIAT%2FFlickr.%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20me%20that%20the%20first%20time%20they%20used%20these%20chemicals%20and%20went%20to%20the%20farm%20the%20next%20day%2C%20they%20saw%20rows%20and%20rows%20of%20dead%20sparrows.%20This%20description%20of%20ecological%20horror%20still%20haunts%20me.%20This%20disgusted%20him%20so%20much%20that%20he%20fell%20ill%20and%20even%20thought%20of%20abandoning%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20logic%20of%20economic%20returns%20eventually%20prevailed%20and%20the%20results%20of%20environmental%20degradation%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20rural%20life%20are%20in%20front%20of%20us.%20Bai%20Gurnaib%20never%20forgot%20that%20a%20phase%20once%20existed%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20which%20was%20healthy%20for%20the%20land%2C%20people%2C%20animals%20and%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20talk%20to%20him%20regularly%20from%20Oxford%20about%20family%20updates%2C%20but%20also%20about%20the%20changing%20economic%20and%20social%20landscape%20of%20rural%20Punjab.%20He%20always%20enquired%20about%20my%20wife%2C%20daughter%20and%20son-in-law%2C%20but%20rarely%20talked%20about%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20changed%20dramatically%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Ffarmers-protest%5C%22%3Efarmers%E2%80%99%20struggle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20told%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20write%20and%20give%20lectures%20in%20support%20of%20the%20farmers.%20I%20know%20that%20what%20you%20write%20and%20say%20gets%20wide%20circulation.%20Send%20me%20copies%20of%20your%20articles%20in%20Punjabi%20and%20video%20lectures%20in%20Punjabi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20took%20every%20minute%20and%20every%20ounce%20of%20my%20energy%20to%20honour%20his%20request.%20His%20death%20leaves%20a%20big%20hole%20in%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Femerging-solidarities-in-the-kisan-andolan%5C%22%3EEmerging%20Solidarities%20in%20the%20Kisan%20Andolan%3A%20How%20Its%20Composition%20Makes%20It%20a%20Role%20Model%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20once%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20a%20research%20project%20to%20collect%20the%20memories%20of%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%2C%20such%20as%20Bai%20Gurnaib%2C%20who%20experienced%20the%20pre-Green%20Revolution%20phase%20of%20agriculture%20and%20rural%20life.%20Their%20views%20about%20the%20Green%20Revolution%20were%20also%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20what%20is%20widely%20believed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20regret%20that%20this%20project%20never%20came%20to%20fruition.%20I%20have%20lost%20a%20brother%20but%20also%20an%20archive%20of%20precious%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20leaves%20a%20beautiful%20legacy%20through%20his%20lovely%20children.%20In%20the%20last%20phase%20of%20his%20life%2C%20Bai%20Gurnaib%20was%20witness%20to%20a%20huge%20socio-economic%20change%20in%20the%20Malwa%20belt%20of%20Punjab%2C%20with%20unpredictable%20political%20consequences%2C%20namely%20the%20mass%20migration%20of%20the%20educated%20Punjabi%20youth%20to%20the%20West.%20All%20his%20adult%20grandchildren%20have%20migrated%20and%20his%20only%20great-grandson%20was%20born%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20experienced%20two%20internal%20migrations%20%E2%80%93%20from%20one%20village%20to%20another%20and%20then%20from%20the%20village%20to%20Faridkot%2C%20the%20town%20named%20after%20Baba%20Farid%20%E2%80%93%20he%20had%20mixed%20feelings%20about%20the%20migration%20of%20the%20youth%20in%20his%20own%20family%20and%20beyond.%20Whether%20in%20India%20or%20abroad%2C%20his%20life%20story%20of%20devotion%2C%20hard%20work%20and%20care%20remains%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration%20to%20his%20big%20network%20of%20family%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpritam-singh%5C%22%3EPritam%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20Emeritus%20Professor%20at%20the%20Oxford%20Brookes%20Business%20School%2C%20Oxford%2C%20UK%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691674538000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10182950%2FGurnaib-Singh-Gill.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fgurnaib-singh-gill-tribute-rural-history-punjab%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pritam%20Singh%20pays%20tribute%20to%20his%20brother.%20whose%20life%20covered%20many%20shifts%20in%20the%20contemporary%20economic%2C%20social%20and%20cultural%20history%20of%20Punjab%2C%20especially%20its%20rural%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fgurnaib-singh-gill-tribute-rural-history-punjab%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rare%20Pics%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20Musical%20Past%3A%20A%20Raga%20Reaches%20Outer%20Space%2C%20Nation%E2%80%99s%20First%20Rock%20Band%20%26%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20were%20to%20chronicle%20all%20the%20music%20genres%20that%20India%20has%20given%