7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22After%20Yuvraj%20Nobody....%5C%22%3A%20Rohit%20Admits%20Grim%20Situation%20Ahead%20of%20World%20Cup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20in%20India%20is%20less%20that%20two%20months%20away%20but%20the%20hosts'%20team%20combination%20is%20nowhere%20close%20to%20being%20sorted.%20Much%20like%20the%202019%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20one%20slot%20which%20is%20bothering%20India%20is%20the%20No.%204%20slot.%20%C2%A0No%20batter%20has%20succeeded%20in%20settling%20into%20the%20vital%20number%20four%20slot%20in%20the%20Indian%20ODI%20team%20since%20the%20retirement%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuvraj%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F456-yuvraj-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuvraj%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20raising%20serious%20concerns%20before%20the%20World%20Cup.%20With%20the%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20less%20than%20two%20months%20away%2C%20India%20are%20struggling%20to%20find%20a%20batter%20for%20the%20No.%204%20slot%2C%20something%20that%20has%20also%20troubled%20them%20in%20the%20previous%20edition%20in%202019%20in%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20comeback%20trail%20after%20a%20long%20injury%20layoff%2C%20did%20well%20in%20his%2020%20matches%20at%20No.%204%2C%20scoring%20805%20runs%20at%2047.35%20with%20two%20centuries%20and%20five%20fifties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20No.%204%20has%20been%20an%20issue%20for%20us%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20After%20Yuvi%20(Yuvraj%20Singh)%2C%20nobody%20has%20come%20and%20settled%20themselves%20in.%20But%2C%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20Shreyas%20(Iyer)%20has%20actually%20batted%20at%20No.%204%20and%20he%20has%20done%20well%20%E2%80%94%20his%20numbers%20are%20really%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20La%20Liga%20event%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20injuries%20have%20given%20him%20a%20bit%20of%20trouble%3B%20he%20has%20been%20out%20for%20a%20while%20and%20that%20is%20honestly%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20last%204-5%20years.%20A%20lot%20of%20these%20guys%20have%20got%20injured%20and%20you%20will%20always%20see%20a%20new%20guy%20coming%20and%20playing%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20captain%20said%20the%20percentage%20of%20injuries%20to%20players%20in%20key%20positions%20has%20hampered%20the%20team%20in%20the%20longer%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20percentage%20of%20injuries%20that%20have%20happened%20in%20the%20last%204-5%20years%2C%20it%20is%20massive.%20When%20the%20players%20get%20injured%20or%20are%20not%20available%2C%20you%20try%20doing%20different%20things%20with%20different%20players%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20what%20I%20have%20to%20say%20about%20No.%204%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20before%2C%20when%20I%20was%20not%20the%20captain%2C%20I%20was%20watching%20no%3F%20There%20were%20so%20many%20guys%20who%20came%20in%20and%20went%20out.%20But%20injuries%20kept%20them%20away%20or%20they%20were%20not%20available%20or%20someone%20lost%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691672820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2Fg8luj4d8_rohit-sharma-yuvraj-singh-instagram_625x300_08_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fafter-yuvraj-singh-nobody-rohit-sharma-admits-grim-situation-ahead-of-asia-cup-world-cup-4286709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yuvraj%20Singh%20and%20Rohit%20Sharm