standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgautam-adani-prepared-to-go-solo-on-hydrogen-mega-project-in-india-123081000471_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2286%20Years%20Ago%2C%20Launching%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%2C%20Gandhi%20Had%20Warned%20Us%20of%20Our%20Current%20State%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ago%20we%20celebrated%20the%2086th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20historic%20Quit%20India%20movement%20launched%20on%20August%209%2C%201942%2C%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20from%20British%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%20core%20goal%2C%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20had%20huge%20dimensions%20covering%20freedom%20of%20press%20and%20democracy%20which%20are%20in%20serious%20danger%20in%20our%20country%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20before%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20was%20launched%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Congress%20Committee%20on%20August%207%2C%201942%2C%20very%20presciently%20said%20that%20apart%20from%20helping%20India%20attain%20freedom%2C%20the%20historic%20movement%20would%20usher%20in%20democracy%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20raised%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98Quit%20India%E2%80%99%20the%20people%20in%20India%20who%20were%20then%20feeling%20despondent%20felt%20I%20had%20placed%20before%20them%20a%20new%20thing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20real%20freedom%20you%20will%20have%20to%20come%20together%20and%20such%20coming%20together%20will%20create%20true%20democracy%20%E2%80%93democracy%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20has%20not%20been%20so%20far%20witnessed%2C%20nor%20have%20there%20been%20any%20attempts%20made%20for%20such%20type%20of%20true%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20he%20had%20read%20a%20good%20deal%20about%20the%20French%20Revolution%20and%20went%20through%20Thomas%20Carlyle%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20jail.%20He%20added%20that%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20had%20explained%20to%20him%20all%20about%20the%20Russian%20revolution%20as%20well.%20He%20held%20that%20though%20those%20were%20fights%20for%20the%20people%2C%20they%20were%20not%20fights%20for%20the%20kind%20of%20real%20democracy%20which%20he%20envisaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmeans%20every%20man%20is%20his%20own%20master%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fquit-india-movement-narendra-modi-gandhi-netaji%5C%22%3ERemembering%20Those%20Who%20Opposed%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20%E2%80%93%20And%20Who%20Didn%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20read%20sufficient%20history%20and%20I%20did%20not%20see%20such%20an%20experiment%20on%20so%20large%20a%20scale%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20democracy%20by%20non-violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20understand%20these%20things%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20will%20forget%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Muslims%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnity%20under%20attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20tragic%20that%20as%20we%20celebrate%20the%20anniversary%20of%20that%20epoch%20making%20Movement%2C%20India%20is%20getting%20polarised%20by%20the%20pronouncement%20of%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime%20of%20our%20country.%20These%20leaders%20employ%20binary-based%20Hindu-Muslim%20narratives%20to%20divide%20people%20along%20religious%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20distinctions%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20which%20Gandhi%20hoped%20would%20be%20eliminated%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20democracy%20following%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20have%20been%20accentuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20communal%20and%20sinister%20happenings%20in%20Nuh%20in%20Haryana%20manifested%20in%20the%20form%20of%20targeted%20attack%20on%20Muslims%20by%20Hindutva%20forces.%20The%20latter%20organised%20a%20religious%20procession%20predominantly%20through%20Muslim%20dominated%20areas%20and%20used%20provocative%20slogans%20against%20them.%20Hatred%20was%20carefully%20cultivated%20against%20Muslims%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20be%20subjected%20to%20spiralling%20violence%20and%20exclusion%20on%20account%20of%20their%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brutal%20employment%20of%20bulldozers%20by%20the%20Haryana%20government%20to%20demolish%20the%20homes%20and%20other%20establishments%20of%20Muslims%20rendered%20hundreds%20of%20them%20homeless.%20Their%20sources%20of%20livelihood%20were%20wiped%20out%20in%20a%20callous%2C%20merciless%20and%20unauthorised%20manner.%20The%20havoc%20wrought%20on%20Muslims%20was%20of%20such%20magnitude%20that%20it%20prompted%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20to%20take%20%3Cem%3Esuo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emotu%3C%2Fem%3E%20cognisance%20of%20the%20crisis.%20It%20asked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-hc-halts-demolitions-in-nuh-owaisi-accuses-khattar-administration-of-targeting-muslims%5C%22%3Eif%20the%20move%20was%20an%20exercise%20of%20%E2%80%9Cethnic%20cleansing%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20as%20we%20celebrate%20the%2086th%20anniversary%20of%20Quit%20India%20Movement%2C%20a%20high%20court%20of%20our%20country%20is%20interrogating%20a%20political%20regime%20for%20its%20actions%20against%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20challenging%20vision%20of%20forgetting%20Hindu-Muslim%20differences%20is%20now%20reversed%20with%20adverse%20consequences%20for%20the%20might%20and%20majesty%20of%20our%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20and%20faith%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20speech%20Gandhi%20firmly%20said%20that%20work%20would%20not%20finish%20with%20the%20attainment%20of%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20categorically%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20place%20for%20dictators%20in%20our%20scheme%20of%20things%E2%80%9D.%20Such%20an%20articulation%20flowed%20from%20his%20conviction%20in%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20object%20is%20to%20achieve%20independence%20and%20whoever%20can%20take%20up%20the%20reins%20may%20do%20so%E2%80%9D.%20He%20forcefully%20pleaded%20that%20the%20people%20decide%20to%20whom%20power%20would%20be%20given%20and%20it%20might%20be%20that%20Parsis%20or%20those%20whose%20names%20were%20never%20heard%20within%20Congress%20circles%20would%20be%20entrusted%20with%20the%20power%20to%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20it%20clear%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20not%20feel%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20those%20who%20fought%20for%20it%20were%20Hindus%20and%20the%20number%20of%20Muslims%20and%20Parsis%20in%20the%20fight%20was%20small.%E2%80%9D%20Advocating%20for%20a%20change%20of%20mentality%20after%20getting%20freedom%2C%20he%20emphasised%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20the%20slightest%20communal%20taint%20in%20your%20minds%2C%20keep%20off%20the%20struggle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20earnest%20pleadings%20that%20elimination%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20differences%20and%20removal%20of%20the%20slightest%20communal%20taint%20formed%20the%20backdrop%20against%20which%20Quit%20India%20was%20launched.%20Those%20defining%20attributes%20are%20now%20being%20annihilated%20by%20those%20wielding%20state%20apparatus%20in%20India%20and%20they%2C%20through%20their%20calibrated%20measures%2C%20are%20spelling%20ruin%20to%20those%20very%20founding%20ideals%20of%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutlining%20the%20core%20objective%20of%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement%20as%20freedom%20of%20our%20country%20from%20British%20rule%20Gandhi%20had%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCommunal%20unity%20must%20follow%20as%20day%20follows%20night%20when%20the%20night%20of%20foreign%20domination%20is%20gone%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-violence-rpf-constables-murder-new-phase-anti-muslim-hate%5C%22%3ENuh%20Violence%20and%20RPF%20Constable%E2%80%99s%20Murder%20Spree%20Reveal%20a%20New%20Phase%20of%20Anti-Muslim%20Hate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20divisiveness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aforementioned%20speech%20at%20the%20AICC%20on%20August%208%2C%201942%2C%20Gandhi%2C%20however%2C%20referred%20to%20%E2%80%9CThose%20Hindus%E2%80%A6like%20Dr.%20Moonje%20and%20Shri%20Savarkar%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20stated%20that%20they%20%C2%A0believed%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20doctrine%20of%20the%20sword%E2%80%A6to%20keep%20the%20Mussalmans%20under%20Hindu%20domination%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20represent%20that%20section%E2%80%9D%20and%20affirmed%20that%20he%20represented%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20distrust%20the%20Congress%2C%20you%20may%20rest%20assured%20that%20there%20is%20to%20be%20a%20perpetual%20war%20between%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Mussalmans%2C%20and%20the%20country%20will%20be%20doomed%20to%20continue%20warfare%20and%20bloodshed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20India%20is%20being%20pushed%20to%20the%20fearsome%20scenario%20of%20war%20between%20Hindus%20and%20%C2%A0Muslims%20because%20of%20the%20spewing%20of%20communal%20hatred%20by%20the%20powers%20that%20be.%20The%20message%20of%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20centring%20around%20communal%20amity%20and%20unity%20is%20the%20categorical%20imperative%20which%20we%20can%20ignore%20at%20our%20own%20peril.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691661724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fquit-india-movement-communal-polarisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Once%20you%20understand%20these%20things%2C'%20Gandhi%20had%20said%2C%20'you%20will%20forget%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Muslims.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fquit-india-movement-communal-polarisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gadar%202%20and%20OMG%202%20to%20score%20200%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691660786000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102606093%2Cimgsize-42694.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fgadar-2-and-omg-2-clash-sunny-deol-and-akshay-kumar-starrers-tipped-to-bring-hindi-box-office-rs-200-crore-collection-over-independence-weekend%2Farticleshow%2F102605539.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102605539.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20upcoming%20Bollywood%20movies%20Gadar%202%20and%20OMG%202%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20a%20big%20box%20office%20clash%20over%20the%20Independence%20Day%20weekend%20with%20massive%20collections%20estimated%20at%20Rs%20200%20crore%20plus.%20Early%20estimates%20indicate%20that%20Gadar%202%20will%20have%20a%20higher%20opening%20than%20OMG%202%2C%20both%20films%20are%20expected%20to%20earn%20a%20collective%20gross%20of%20Rs%2040-50%20crore%20nett%20on%20Day%201.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20box%20office%20will%20be%20boosted%20by%20collections%20from%20the%20release%20of%20Superst