erful%20people%20in%20the%20country.%20They%20have%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20the%20rule%20book%20if%20politicians%20demand%20illegal%20action%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EWhy%20is%20it%20that%20officers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fwhos-prabhakar-chaudhary-ips-officer-facing-18th-transfer-in-8-yrs-after-lathicharge-on-kanwariyas%2F1696168%2F%5C%22%3EPrabhakar%20Chaudhary%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20who%20stopped%20a%20procession%20of%20Kanwariyas%20in%20Bareilly%20from%20going%20down%20an%20unauthorised%20route%20%E2%80%93%20are%20an%20exception%3F%20Either%20all%20our%20officers%20have%20turned%20cowards%20or%20they%20themselves%20believe%20in%20the%20bulldozer%20as%20a%20form%20of%20punishment%20for%20Muslims.%20What%20does%20it%20say%20about%20us%20or%20the%20Indian%20state%3F%20And%2C%20about%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20that%20does%20not%20follow%20the%20process%2C%20as%20defined%20in%20the%20rule%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105412%2F1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105412%2F1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105412%2F1-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105412%2F1-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStones%20and%20bricks%20used%20in%20the%20riots%20can%20be%20seen%20everywhere%20in%20Nuh.%20Photo%3A%20Atul%20Ashok%20Howale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EWhen%20not%20subjected%20to%20physical%20violence%2C%20Muslims%20are%20abused%2C%20insulted%2C%20and%20humiliated%20using%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20physical%20assemblies.%20Hate%20assemblies%20and%20processions%20take%20place%20despite%20prohibitory%20orders.%20Political%20leaders%20indulge%20in%20anti-Muslim%20hate%20slogans%2C%20directly%20and%20as%20dog%20whistles.%20Even%20the%20courts%20seem%20to%20be%20tolerant%20towards%20them.%20They%20argue%20that%20their%20anti-Muslim%20speech%20is%20only%20meant%20to%20excite%20and%20enthuse%20their%20constituency%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-something-is-said-with-a-smile-then-there-is-no-criminality-delhi-hc-on-hate-speech%5C%22%3Edoes%20not%20actually%20mean%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20this%20view%20is%20dominant%20among%20the%20police%2C%20administration%2C%20and%20judiciary%2C%20the%20chances%20of%20hate%20spreaders%20being%20restrained%20or%20getting%20prosecuted%20are%20very%20slim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3EHaryana%20Violence%3A%20How%20Provocative%20Videos%20and%20a%20Background%20of%20Hate%20Preceded%20the%20Nuh%20Riots%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20are%20expected%20to%20allow%20the%20hate%20spreaders%20to%20enjoy%20their%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20restrain%20themselves.%20Wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20Haryana%20administration%20apprised%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Ehate%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%20circulating%20before%20the%20yatra%20which%20led%20to%20violence%20in%20Nuh%3F%20Why%20did%20the%20administration%20not%20take%20the%20threat%20of%20violence%20seriously%3F%20Why%20did%20the%20police%20not%20think%20it%20necessary%20to%20at%20least%20lodge%20cases%20against%20those%20who%20made%20the%20videos%20and%20others%20who%20circulated%20them%3F%20Was%20the%20administration%20helpless%20or%20unwilling%3F%20Why%20was%20it%20not%20interested%20in%20assuaging%20the%20feelings%20of%20Muslims%2C%20against%20whom%20open%20threats%20were%20being%20issued%3F%20Why%20did%20it%20not%20matter%20to%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%E2%80%99s%20job%20is%20to%20maintain%20peace.%20But%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20this%20has%20taken%20on%20a%20warped%20form.%20For%20administrations%2C%20%E2%80%98maintaining%20peace%E2%80%99%20can%20also%20mean%20letting%20the%20Hindutvawadis%20do%20what%20they%20want%2C%20by%20not%20resisting%20or%20restraining%20them.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20is%20not%20arresting%20those%20who%20claim%20that%20they%20are%20demolishing%20%3Cem%3Emazars%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20Is%20it%20not%20true%20that%20demolishing%20mazars%20amounts%20to%20a%20breach%20of%20peace%3F%20But%2C%20the%20moment%20Muslims%20resist%20or%20oppose%20this%2C%20a%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharidwar-anti-muslim-hate-speech-laws-broken%5C%22%3Ehate%20assemblies%20calling%20for%20the%20annihilation%20of%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20seen%20as%20disturbing%20the%20peace.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fseven-incidents-across-india-where-the-hindutva-brigade-disrupted-christmas-celebrations%5C%22%3Epeople%20barge%20in%20when%20Christmas%20is%20being%20celebrated%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20church%20and%20raise%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20slogans%2C%20it%20is%20not%20seen%20as%20a%20problem%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20breach%20of%20peace%20only%20when%20these%20elements%20are%20stopped%20from%20doing%20what%20they%20want.%20The%20police%20officer%20Prabhakar%20Chaudhary%20stopped%20the%20VHP%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20from%20playing%20loud%20music%20outside%20a%20mosque%20in%20Bareilly%20and%20creating%20a%20ruckus%20there.%20He%20ordered%20a%20lathi%20charge%20to%20disperse%20them.%20As%20a%20punishment%2C%20the%20officer%20was%20transferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EImagine%20a%20similar%20situation%20in%20which%20a%20group%20of%20Muslims%20do%20what%20the%20VHP%20or%20Bajrang%20Dal%20do%20regularly.%20Would%20they%20be%20allowed%3F%20The%20fate%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fazam-khan-conviction-hate-speech-case-set-aside%5C%22%3EAzam%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20before%20us.%20His%20legislative%20assembly%20membership%20has%20been%20taken%20away%20after%20he%20was%20sentenced%20to%20three%20years%20in%20jail%20for%20a%20hate%20speech%20against%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%20Just%20recollect%20some%20of%20the%20speeches%20made%20by%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20prime%20minister.%20If%20the%20same%20standards%20were%20applied%20to%20them%2C%20they%20would%20also%20be%20in%20jail.%20But%2C%20we%20know%20that%20will%20never%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20targeting%20of%20Muslims%20on%20TV%20channels%20every%20day%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20legitimate%20exercise%20of%20free%20speech.%20No%20breach%20of%20the%20peace%20here!%20Muslims%20should%20just%20switch%20off%20the%20TV%20if%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20abuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeave%20aside%20the%20organised%20hate%20campaigns%2C%20now%20unaffiliated%20individuals%20promote%20this%20hate%20campaign%20voluntarily%20in%20their%20family%20or%20school%20or%20neighbourhood%20groups%20and%20friend%20circles.%20Everything%20remains%20peaceful%20till%20the%20hate%20is%20challenged%20by%20some%20%E2%80%98crazy%E2%80%99%20member%20of%20the%20group.%20Then%20she%20or%20he%20is%20blamed%20for%20disturbing%20the%20tranquility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%2