nta-das-speech-123081000087_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RBI%20MPC%20Meeting%20Live%20Updates%3A%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20begins%20policy%20statement%2C%20catch%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-mpc-meet-10-august-2023-live-news-monetary-policy-reserve-bank-of-india-shaktikanta-das-speech-123081000087_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Frbi-mpc-meet-10-august-2023-live-news-monetary-policy-reserve-bank-of-india-shaktikanta-das-speech-123081000087_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Frbi-mpc-meet-10-august-2023-live-news-monetary-policy-reserve-bank-of-india-shaktikanta-das-speech-123081000087_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Treatment%20for%20the%20Dead%2C%20Discharge%20Before%20Surgery%20and%20the%20Many%20Problems%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F29145146%2Fabdm.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20report%20on%20the%20assessment%20of%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(PMJAY)%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20two%20components%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20has%20shown%20that%20despite%20being%20a%20highly%20important%20intervention%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20address%20health%20needs%2C%20it%20remains%20riddled%20with%20corruption%20of%20various%20kinds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20funding%20of%20the%20scheme%20is%20shared%20between%20the%20state%20governments%20and%20the%20Union%20in%20the%20ratio%20of%2060%3A40.%20At%20the%20Union%20government-level%2C%20the%20National%20Health%20Authority%20(NHA)%20is%20responsible%20for%20scheme%20implementation.%20In%20states%2C%20the%20job%20has%20to%20be%20done%20through%20state%20health%20authorities%20(SHAs)%20and%20district%20implementations%20units.%20The%20scheme%20aims%20to%20provide%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20family%20as%20per%20the%20strict%20criteria%20defined%20in%20the%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdashboard.pmjay.gov.in%2Fpmj%2F%23%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENHA%20database%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%2024.42%20crore%20beneficiaries%20have%20been%20registered%20for%20the%20scheme%20till%20date%20and%20Rs%2067%2C456.21%20crore%20has%20been%20spent%20on%20their%20hospital%20admissions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAG%20assessment%20included%20the%20time%20period%20of%20September%202018%20to%20March%202021%20%E2%80%93%20part%20of%20which%20coincides%20with%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20The%20auditor%20test%20checked%20964%20hospitals%20in%20161%20districts%20of%20all%2028%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20(UTs).%20Delhi%2C%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%20have%20opted%20out%20of%20this%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20CAG%20report%20on%20the%20PMJAY.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20auditors%20found%20large%20scale%20corruption%20in%20insurance%20claims%20settlement.%20It%20reported%20that%20not%20enough%20validation%20was%20done%20by%20the%20SHAs%20before%20releasing%20the%20claims%20to%20the%20hospitals%20which%20were%20empanelled%20under%20the%20scheme.%20It%20noted%20that%20in%202.25%20lakh%20cases%2C%20the%20date%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98surgery%E2%80%99%20done%20was%20shown%20to%20be%20later%20than%20the%20date%20of%20discharge.%20Of%20all%20such%20cases%2C%20more%20than%201.79%20lakh%20were%20found%20in%20Maharashtra%20for%20which%20the%20claimed%20amount%20was%20over%20Rs%20300%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20other%20instances%2C%20the%20hospitals%20had%20made%20claims%20and%20the%20SHAs%20had%20transferred%20money%20for%20dates%20even%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebefore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20scheme.%20The%20payments%20were%20made%20to%20hospitals%20in%20some%20cases%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eprior%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20submission%20of%20claims.%20In%20other%20cases%2C%20patients%20above%2018%20years%20of%20age%20were%20given%20treatment%20under%20%E2%80%98paediatric%20speciality%20packages%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fayushman-bharat-trivialises-indias-quest-for-universal-health-care%5C%22%3EAyushman%20Bharat%20Trivialises%20India%E2%80%99s%20Quest%20for%20Universal%20Health%20Care%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audit%20also%20found%20that%20in%2045%2C846%20claims%2C%20the%20date%20of%20discharge%20was%20earlier%20than%20date%20of%20admission.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20audit%20found%20several%20cases%20where%20one%20patient%20had%20been%20shown%20to%20be%20hospitalised%20in%20multiple%20hospitals%20at%20one%20given%20point%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhs%20of%20claims%20continued%20to%20be%20made%20against%20some%20who%20had%20been%20shown%20as%20%E2%80%98deceased%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20data%20in%20the%20Transaction%20Management%20System%20(TMS)%20showed%20that%2088%2C760%20patients%20had%20died%20during%20treatment.%20And%20yet%2C%202%2C14%2C923%20claims%20were%20shown%20as%20paid%20in%20respect%20of%20%E2%80%98fresh%20treatments%E2%80%99%20given%20to%20these%20dead%20%E2%80%98patients%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20Almost%20Rs%207%20crore%20was%20spent%20towards%20settling%20these%20claims%20in%2024%20states%20and%20UTs.%20The%20maximum%20number%C2%A0%20of%20such%20cases%20were%20observed%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELakhs%20of%20cards%20issued%20to%20beneficiaries%20were%20cancelled%20just%20as%20they%20were%20registered%20owing%20to%20malpractices.%20But%20the%20TMS%20%E2%80%93%20the%20system%20in%20place%20%E2%80%93%20failed%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20pre-authorisation%20request%20for%20claims%20by%20hospitals%20made%20against%20these%20cards%20be%20restricted.%20As%20such%2C%20Rs%2071.47%20lakh%20were%20paid%20towards%20beneficiaries%20registered%20as%20per%20these%20%E2%80%98disabled%E2%80%99%20cards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20caution%20against%20bogus%2011.04%20lakh%20beneficiaries%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20NHA%20generated%20many%20alerts%20to%20the%20SHAs.%20The%20SHAs%20could%20investigate%20only%207.07%20lakh%20cards.%20The%20highest%20number%20of%20such%20fraud%20claims%20were%20made%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Meghalaya%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20unique%20ID%3A%20Several%20beneficiaries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20instances%20of%20graft%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20this%20scheme%20was%20found%20in%20registration%20and%20identification%20of%20beneficiaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20stipulates%20that%20a%20unique%20PMJAY%20ID%20should%20be%20issued%20to%20beneficiaries%20once%20verification%20is%20complete.%20The%20audit%20discovered%20that%201.57%20unique%20IDs%20appeared%20more%20than%20once%20in%20the%20database.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20all%20these%20IDs%20were%20duplicated.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20circumstances%2C%20possibility%20of%20presence%20of%20ineligible%20beneficiaries%20in%20the%20Beneficiary%20Identification%20System%20%5BBIS%5D%20database%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20Aadhaar%20numbers%2C%20the%20system%20also%20utilises%20the%20phone%20numbers%20of%20beneficiaries.%20The%20audit%20brought%20to%20light%20that%20there%20were%20large%20numbers%20of%20beneficiaries%20registered%20against%20the%20same%20or%20invalid%20mobile%20number.%20For%20example%2C%207.5%20lakh%20beneficiaries%20were%20registered%20against%20the%20%E2%80%989999999999%E2%80%99%20mobile%20number%20and%20another%201.4%20lakh%20under%20the%20%E2%80%988888888888%E2%80%99%20number.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20CAG%20report%20was%20released%2C%20an%20anonymous%20source%20of%20Union%20health%20and%20family%20welfare%20ministry%20has%20been%20quoted%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Findia%2F7-lakh-people-1-phone-number-auditor-flags-discrepancies-in-health-scheme-article-102582047%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20scheme%20only%20used%20mobile%20numbers%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20beneficiaries%20in%20case%20of%20any%20need%20and%20for%20collecting%20feedback%20regarding%20treatment%2C%20rather%20than%20for%20verification%20purposes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fayushman-bharat-scheme-inactive-hospitals%5C%22%3EOnly%20Two-Thirds%20of%20Hospitals%20Under%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Scheme%20Active%20Now%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20unnamed%20official%20went%20on%20to%20add%3A%20%E2%80%9CAB-PMJAY%20identifies%20the%20beneficiary%20through%20Aadhaar%20identification%20wherein%20the%20beneficiary%20undergoes%20the%20process%20of%20mandatory%20Aadhaar%20based%20e-KYC.%20The%20details%20fetched%20from%20the%20Aadhaar%20database%20are%20matched%20with%20the%20source%20database%20and%20accordingly%2C%20the%20request%20for%20Ayushman%20card%20is%20approved%20or%20rejected%20based%20on%20the%20beneficiary%20details.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20Aadhaar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20according%20to%20the%20audit%20report%20not%20all%20is%20well%20with%20Aadhaar%20identification%20either.%20Two%20registrations%20each%20were%20found%20to%20be%20made%20against%2018%20Aadhaar%20cards.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%204%2C761%20registrations%20were%20made%20against%20seven%20Aadhaar%20numbers%2C%20the%20audit%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20further%20surprising%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20as%20per%20the%20scheme%20guidelines%2C%20the%20SHAs%20have%20to%20send%20SMS%20notifications%20to%20the%20contact%20number%20provided%20to%20check%20their%20eligibility.%20So%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20such%20large-scale%20duplication%20of%20numbers%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20as%20to%20whether%20those%20SMS%20notifications%20were%20indeed%20sent%2C%20and%20if%20they%20were%20sent%2C%20who%20received%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMobile%20numbers%20are%20significant%20for%20searching%20records%20related%20to%20any%20beneficiary%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edatabase%2C%20who%20may%20approach%20the%20registration%20desk%20without%20the%20ID%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20auditors%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%20of%20loss%20of%20e-card%2C%20identification%20of%20the%20beneficiary%20may%20also%20become%20difficult.%20This%20may%20result%20in%20denial%20of%20scheme%20benefits%20to%20eligible%20beneficiaries%20as%20well%20as%20denial%20of%20pre-%20and%20post-admission%20communication%20causing%20inconvenience%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20go%20on%20to%20add.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20in%20its%20statement%20the%20ministry%20tried%20to%20downplay%20the%20duplication%20of%20mobile%20numbers%2C%20the%20audit%20report%20says%20the%20NHA%20had%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20with%20audit%20observation%E2%80%9D%20and%20assured%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20deployment%20of%20BIS%202.0%20would%20arrest%20this%20practice.%20And%20as%20such%2C%20the%20data%20entry%20operators%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20enter%20%E2%80%9Crandom%20numbers%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20registration%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHospital%20empanelment%20done%20without%20checks%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NHA%20database%2C%2027%2C649%20hospitals%20have%20been%20empanelled%20across%20India%20for%20providing%20services%20under%20this%20scheme.%20All%20public%20facilities%20with%20capability%20of%20providing%20inpatient%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eservices%20(community%20health%20centre-level%20and%20above)%20are%20deemed%20empanelled.%20As%20such%2C%20a%20little%20over%2015%2C000%20public%20and%2012%2C000%20private%20healthcare%20facilities%20are%20part%20of%20this%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20Empaneled%20Healthcare%20Provider%20(EHCP)%20has%20to%20fulfil%20criteria%20like%20the%20presence%20of%20round-the-clock%20support%20systems%20required%20for%20services%20like%20pharmacy%2C%20blood%20bank%2C%20laboratory%2C%20dialysis%20unit%2C%20post%20operative%20services%2C%20ICU%20care%20etc.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%20Bihar%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20physical%20verification%20reports%20of%2023%20EHCPs%20disclosed%20that%2016%20of%20them%20did%20not%20fulfil%20the%20essential%20criteria.%20Other%20than%20Bihar%3B%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20Assam%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Puducherry%2C%20Tripura%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20figured%20in%20this%20list%20of%20states%20where%20hospitals%20got%20empanelled%20and%20failed%20to%20serve%20the%20purpose.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20deficiencies%20such%20as%20medical%20equipment%20being%20out%20of%20order%2C%20lack%20of%20basic%20infrastructure%20such%20as%20IPD%20Beds%2C%20Operation%20Theatres%2C%20ICU%20care%20with%20ventilator%20support%20systems%2C%20Pharmacy%2C%20Dialysis%20Unit%2C%20Blood%20banks%2C%20Round-the%20clock%20Ambulance%20Services%20etc.%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%20the%20auditors%20found%20that%20without%20doing%20enough%20checks%20and%20without%20the%20mandated%20physical%20inspection%2C%20respective%20district%20empanelment%20committees%20gave%20a%20go-ahead%20for%20the%20empanelment%20of%20163%20hospitals.%20Tripura%20ranked%20first%20with%20103%20such%20EHCPs%20followed%20by%20Uttarakhand%20(43)%20and%20Manipur%20(17).%20The%20NHA%20explained%20that%20the%20inspection%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20done%20at%20these%20facilities%20owing%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpandemic%20conditions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20hospitals%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20after%20being%20empanelled%20for%20a%20certain%20set%20of%20fixed%20services%2C%20failed%20in%20providing%20them.%20For%20instance%2C%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20audit%20noted%20that%201%2C113%20types%20of%20treatment%20facilities%C2%A0%20were%20not%20provided%20in%20the%20hospitals%20located%20in%20Nandurbar%2C%20Washim%2C%20Osmanabad%2C%20Gadchiroli%20and%20Palghar%20Districts%2C%20and%20beneficiaries%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20other%20districts%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20states%2C%20lack%20of%20speciality%20services%20necessitated%20the%20beneficiaries%20to%20move%20far%20off%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eplaces%20which%20causes%20hardship%20and%20great%20amount%20of%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20beneficiaries%20and%20may%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Elead%20to%20out-of-pocket%20expenditure%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%20Incidentally%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20purposes%20of%20the%20PMJAY%20is%20to%20reduce%20the%20out-of-pocket%20expenditure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fexplainer-ayushman-bharat-digital-mission-health-id-aadhaar-records%5C%22%3EAll%20You%20Need%20to%20Know%20on%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Digital%20Mission%2C%20Health%20IDs%20and%20Personal%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMissing%20hospitals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20existence%20of%20hospitals%20in%20the%20empanelled%20list%20did%20not%20necessarily%20translate%20into%20even%20their%20existence%20in%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20forget%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20services%20provided.%20In%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20for%20example%2C%20out%20of%201%2C421%20empanelled%20EHCPs%2C%20half%20of%20them%20submitted%20zero%20claims%20thus%20indicating%20they%20were%20not%20providing%20PMJAY%20services%20at%20all.%20While%2C%20another%2081%20of%20them%20submitted%20only%200-5%20claims.%20Such%20examples%20were%20found%20in%20other%20states%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20accepting%20the%20observation%2C%20the%20NHA%20stated%20(August%202022)%20that%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EEHCPs%20were%20reluctant%20to%20provide%20the%20services%20to%20PMJAY%20beneficiaries%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20audit%20report%20said%2C%20though%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20clarify%20the%20share%20of%20public%20and%20private%20facilities%20who%20were%20reluctant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20did%20say%20what%20many%20experts%20and%20health%20activists%20have%20suggested%20so%20far%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20strong%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20public%20hospitals%20to%20improve%20and%20upgrade%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eexisting%20health%20facilities%20in%20accordance%20with%20prescribed%20criteria%20%5Bof%20the%20PMJAY%20scheme%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20also%20limits%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme%20is%20the%20number%20of%20EHCPs%20empanelled%20vis-a-vis%20the%20number%20of%20beneficiaries.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Bihar%2C%20100%25%20eligible%20people%20have%20been%20registered%20under%20the%20scheme.%20But%20there%20are%20only%201.8%20EHCPs%20per%20lakh%20population%20%E2%80%93%20as%20against%2026.6%20in%20Goa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20EHCPs%20were%20also%20found%20to%20be%20indulging%20in%20various%20malpractices.%20In%20Assam%2C%2018%20EHCPs%20provided%20treatments%20for%20non-empanelled%20specialities%20to%201%2C149%20beneficiaries%20for%20which%20total%20claims%20amounting%20to%20Rs%201.27%20crore%20were%20paid%20to%20the%20hospitals.%20After%20the%20admission%20of%20the%20patient%2C%20from%20diagnosis%20to%20treatment%2C%20everything%20has%20to%20be%20cashless%20for%20patients.%20And%20yet%2C%20hospitals%20were%20found%20to%20be%20demanding%20money%20for%20different%20requirements.%20These%2C%20and%20other%20such%20acts%20of%20omission%2C%20have%20also%20led%20to%20SHAs%20taking%20the%20hospitals%20off%20the%20empanelled%20list.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%2011%20states%2C%20241%20hospitals%20were%20de-empanelled%20from%20the%20PMJAY%20either%20voluntarily%20or%20due%20to%20low%20performance%20and%20malpractices%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%20But%20in%20certain%20instances%2C%20such%20a%20step%20did%20not%20ensure%20stalling%20the%20payments.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20one%20Ananya%20Memorial%20Hospital%20was%20suspended%20in%20August%202019.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20Bihar%20SHA%20paid%20it%20Rs%2067%2C900%20between%202018-20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20shoddy%20supervision%20by%20the%20SHAs%20have%20also%20led%20to%20circumstances%20where%20they%20have%20paid%20excess%20amounts%20to%20the%20hospitals.%20The%20audit%20found%20that%20in%20four%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20%E2%80%93%20excess%20payments%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2057.53%20crore%20were%20made.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELastly%2C%20the%20auditors%20blamed%20the%20NHA%20for%20doing%20enough%20supervision%20over%20SHAs%20and%20releasing%20funds%20for%20them%20even%20when%20they%20had%20not%20spent%20their%20own%20share%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20as%20per%20guidelines%2C%20or%20when%20the%20grants%20were%20lying%20unspent%20with%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-national-health-agency-to-authority%5C%22%3EFrom%20National%20Health%20%E2%80%98Agency%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98Authority%E2%80%99%3A%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Body%20Restructured%20Yet%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20the%20first%20red%20flag%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20this%20report%20does%20raise%20many%20red%20flags%20about%20the%20scheme%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20one.%20In%20fact%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fhealth%2Famp%2Fa-year-of-ayushman-bharat-46-5-lakh-treated-action-against-341-hospitals-for-frauds-67019%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%20annual%20report%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20which%20was%20published%20in%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20pointed%20to%20similar%20frauds.%20The%20subsequent%20annual%20reports%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20quantum%20of%20frauds%20and%20made%20the%20relevant%20database%20inaccessible%20to%20the%20public.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20answering%20a%20question%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20last%20year%2C%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20of%20Union%20health%20ministry%20Bharti%20Pravi%20Pawar%20did%20say%20that%20210%20hospitals%20had%20been%20%E2%80%98de-empanelled%E2%80%99%20and%20another%20188%20suspended%20from%20the%20PMJAY%20services.%20Even%20a%20penalty%20of%20Rs%C2%A0%2021%20crores%20had%20been%20levied%20on%20them%20but%20recovery%20worth%20Rs%209.5%20crore%20could%20only%20be%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10080577%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epaper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20titled%20%E2%80%98Critical%20Analysis%20of%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Publicly%20Funded%20Health%20Insurance%20Program%E2%80%99%20published%20in%20February%202023%20said%20fraud%20in%20such%20schemes%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20contributors%20to%20the%20OOPE.%20%E2%80%9CHealth%20insurance%20fraud%20in%20the%20United%20states%20and%20Europe%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%2010%25%20of%20health-care%20spending.%20In%20India%2C%20that%20number%20could%20be%20as%20high%20as%2035%25%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D1946706%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereplying%20to%20a%20query%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20had%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20two%20days%20ago%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20machine%20learning%C2%A0%20are%20being%20deployed%20to%20detect%20potential%20frauds%20in%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20Pawar%20had%20told%20parliament%20last%20year%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691648054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F29145146%2Fabdm.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20ever%20CAG%20report%20on%20the%20PMJAY%20highlights%20how%20the%20scheme%20has%20been%20riddled%20with%20corruption%20and%20visible%20fraudulence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%3A%20Nuh%20Internet%20Ban%20Extended%20Till%20August%2011%2C%20'Admin%20Failed%20to%20Assess%20Situation'%3A%20Dy%20CM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F04163631%2FDushyant_Chautala_PTI_1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Haryana%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20didn%E2%80%99t%20assess%20the%20situation%20in%20Nuh%20adequately%20while%20describing%20its%20condition%20as%20%E2%80%9Cstill%20critical%20and%20tense%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fsituation-in-nuh-not-assessed-properly-haryana-deputy-chief-minister-dushyant-chautala-internet-ban-extended-till-august-11%2Fcid%2F1957754%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20extended%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20internet%20and%20SMS%20services%20in%20the%20district%20till%20August%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%20ban%20in%20the%20district%20has%20been%20in%20effect%20since%20the%20violence%20erupted%20in%20the%20district%20after%20a%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20procession%20on%20July%2031.%20The%20internet%20suspension%20in%20Nuh%20was%20earlier%20extended%20on%20August%202%2C%20August%205%20and%20August%208%20in%20wake%20of%20the%20escalated%20tensions.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20internet%20in%20Manipur%20was%20suspended%20for%2083%20days%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20in%20the%20state%20on%20May%203%20%E2%80%93%20the%20longest%20internet%20ban%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20DW%20report%2C%20India%20accounted%20for%20approximately%2058%25%20of%20all%20documented%20shutdowns%20globally.%20There%20were%2084%20shutdowns%20in%20the%20country%20in%202022%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20in%20the%20world.%20In%202022%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20experienced%20the%20most%20shutdowns%2C%20at%2049%2C%20including%2016%20back-to-back%20orders%20for%20three-day%20closures%20in%20January%20and%20February%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Chautala%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fsituation-in-nuh-not-assessed-properly-haryana-deputy-chief-minister-dushyant-chautala-internet-ban-extended-till-august-11%2Fcid%2F1957754%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20additional%20DGP%20(law%20and%20order)%20had%20received%20a%20request%20for%20a%20procession%20of%203%2C200%20people%20by%20the%20organisers.%20The%20police%20force%20had%20been%20deployed%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Lack%20of%20assessment%20by%20the%20administration%20which%20could%20not%20assess%20this%20entire%20episode%20properly.%20Nuh%20SP%20(now%20transferred)%20was%20on%20leave%20since%20July%2022%2C%20the%20one%20who%20had%20additional%20charge%20could%20not%20assess%20it%20properly%20and%20the%20officials%20from%20whom%20permission%20(for%20the%20procession)%20was%20taken%20they%20too%20could%20not%20assess%20it%20properly.%20It%20is%20a%20point%20which%20is%20under%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChautala%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20religious%20procession%20had%20not%20given%20a%20proper%20estimation%20of%20the%20expected%20turnout%20to%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20a%20lapse%20which%20may%20have%20led%20to%20the%20violence%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20people%2C%20including%20two%20home%20guards%20and%20a%20cleric%2C%20died%20in%20the%20communal%20clashes.%20A%20total%20of%20312%20persons%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20142%20FIRs%20registered%20so%20far%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20communal%20clashes%20in%20Haryana%2C%20home%20minister%20Anil%20Vij%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20such%20an%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20created%20in%20a%20planned%20manner%20and%20strict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20involved%2C%20be%20it%20a%20minor%20or%20major%2C%20Chautala%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20allegations%20that%20%E2%80%9Cone%20sided%20action%20was%20being%20taken%E2%80%9D%2C%20Chautala%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fsituation-in-nuh-not-assessed-properly-haryana-deputy-chief-minister-dushyant-chautala-internet-ban-extended-till-august-11%2Fcid%2F1957754%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20those%20being%20arrested%20do%20not%20belong%20to%20a%20particular%20caste%20or%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20Haryana%20government%20was%20able%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccontrol%20the%20clashes%20within%20seven%20hours%E2%80%9D%20when%20he%20had%20seen%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20incidents%20continue%20in%20other%20states%20for%20two-three%20weeks.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20it%20was%20our%20efficiency%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20curb%20anti-social%20elements%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chautala%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurfew%20has%20been%20relaxed%20and%20it%20will%20be%20lifted%20gradually%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnuh-demolitions-residents-due-process-damages%5C%22%3ENuh%20Demolitions%3A%20Residents%20Say%20Due%20Process%20Flouted%2C%20Reject%20%E2%80%98Illegal%20Establishments%E2%80%99%20Claim%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20communal%20clashes%20that%20began%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20Nuh%20district%20spread%20to%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20and%20nearby%20areas%20last%20week%20with%20incidents%20reported%20from%20Gurugram%2C%20Faridabad%20and%20Panvel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20violence%2C%20the%20state%20government%20had%20commenced%20a%20demolition%20drive%20in%20Nuh%20which%20was%20stopped%20after%20the%20Panjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20took%20%3Cem%3Esuo%20moto%3C%2Fem%3E%20cognizance%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20ordered%20a%20halt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20body%20Jamiat%20Ulama-i-Hind%20has%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20directions%20for%20rehabilitation%20of%20those%20whose%20homes%20were%20razed%20by%20authorities%20in%20Nuh%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20The%20organisations%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20that%20even%20though%20the%20Panjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20had%20ordered%20a%20halt%20on%20the%20demolitions%2C%20it%20had%20not%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20rehabilitate%20and%20compensate%20those%20who%20were%20displaced%20in%20the%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20government%20has%20transferred%20Nuh%20DSP%20Jai%20Prakash%20to%20Panchkula.%20Prakash%20is%20the%20third%20officer%20after%20SP%20Varun%20Singla%20and%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20Prashant%20Panwar%20who%20have%20been%20transferred%20from%20Nuh%20since%20the%20violence%20erupted%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENuh%20SP%20Narender%20Bijarnia%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20a%20search%20operation%20is%20being%20conducted%20to%20arrest%20the%20accused%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20violence%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2057%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%20and%20170%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20Nuh%20district.%20Apart%20from%201%2C900%20police%20personnel%2C%2031%20companies%20of%20paramilitary%20forces%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20district.%20Posts%20on%20social%20media%20over%20missing%20people%2Fwomen%20are%20misleading%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bijarnia%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691648038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F04163631%2FDushyant_Chautala_PTI_1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22