earning%20fun%20for%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20he%20dropped%20out%20of%20JNU%20to%20start%20teaching%20life%20skills%20and%20grammar%20to%20students.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20went%20to%20JNU%2C%20my%20parents%20expected%20me%20to%20be%20a%20professor%20somewhere%20but%20I%20realised%20I%20could%20do%20a%20lot%20better%20and%20bigger%20by%20teaching%20students.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20best%20education%20started%20after%20I%20left%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20he%20started%20teaching%20in%20a%20coaching%20institute%20in%20Bengaluru.%20As%20part%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20smaller%20towns%20in%20the%20state%20for%20promotional%20programmes%2C%20he%20would%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20interact%20with%20school%20students.%20%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20I%20observed%20the%20horrible%20system%20of%20education%20we%20have.%20I%20asked%20the%20students%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20a%20cloud%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20a%20window%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20they%20looked%20up%20into%20the%20sky.%20They%20had%20no%20idea.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20education%20system%20is%20all%20about%20mugging%20things%20and%20putting%20them%20down.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179905%2Findia-new-education-preschool-primary-curriculum-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERote%20learning%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20itself%20a%20dangerous%20thing%2C%20it%20imparts%20no%20skills%20to%20students.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20rigid%20architecture%20psychologically.%20As%20a%20teacher%2C%20your%20job%20is%20to%20manage%20a%20classroom%20of%20100%20students%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20teaching%20them%2C%20just%20handling%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20classrooms%2C%20the%20person%20who%20sits%20in%20the%20back%20row%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20clown.%20Others%20do%20not%20collaborate%20with%20them.%20Whenever%20a%20backbencher%20stands%20up%2C%20everyone%20bursts%20into%20laughter%2C%20that%20student%20starts%20thinking%20they%20are%20a%20%E2%80%98joker%E2%80%99%20and%20they%20lose%20the%20confidence%20to%20do%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20experiences%20led%20Rennis%20and%20Imma%20(whom%20he%20met%20in%20JNU)%20to%20start%20Ignis%20Careers%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rennis%20and%20his%20team%20have%20taught%20English%20language%20and%20life%20skills%20to%20over%203.5%20lakh%20students%20in%20about%201%2C000%20low-cost%20schools.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1-1691584690-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326821%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERennis%20and%20his%20team%20have%20taught%20English%20language%20and%20life%20skills%20to%20over%203.5%20lakh%20students%20in%20about%201%2C000%20low-cost%20schools.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20classrooms%20fun%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20they%20work%2C%20Rennis%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20form%20a%20small%20group%20of%20say%20five%20students.%20We%20let%20them%20sit%20in%20a%20circle%2C%20not%20rows%20so%20that%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20a%20front%20and%20a%20back-bencher.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20a%20few%20groups%20of%204-5%20students%20each.%20We%20then%20ask%20one%20group%20to%20design%20a%20smart%20village%20with%20the%20best%20sustainable%20technology%20possible%2C%20we%20ask%20another%20group%20to%20redesign%20a%20hospital.%20They%20observe%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20current%20system%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20design%20which%20they%20draw%20on%20a%20chart.%20While%20doing%20that%2C%20they%20build%20design%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20promote%20positive%20interaction%20among%20peers.%20It%20helps%20them%20to%20build%20critical%20awareness%20and%20negotiations%20among%20team%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERennis%20and%20his%20team%20work%20with%20any%20school%20for%20about%20four%20years%2C%20but%20remain%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20school%20to%20trace%20the%20impact.%20For%20instance%2C%20his%20team%20worked%20in%20Banapuram%20village%20of%20Telangana%20in%202010.%20After%20five%20years%20of%20this%20intervention%2C%20he%20says%2C%2090%20percent%20of%20the%20children%20going%20to%20schools%20in%20the%20villages%20were%20enrolled%20in%20higher%20education%20in%20colleges.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20we%20did%20a%20study%20to%20check%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20We%20found%20that%20all%20the%20girls%20were%20still%20in%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20teaching%20the%20students%20through%20interactive%20sessions%2C%20they%20work%20to%20create%20a%20pool%20of%20teachers%20who%20can%20think%20of%20innovative%20ways%20to%20teach%20children%20after%20they%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rennis%20charges%20up%20to%20Rs%20700%20per%20student%20per%20year%20from%20low-cost%20private%20schools.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERennis%20charges%20up%20to%20Rs%20700%20per%20student%20per%20year%20from%20low-cost%20private%20schools.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20Rennis%20says%20a%20trainer%20is%20sent%20to%20a%20school%20once%20every%20week%20and%20is%20provided%20with%20a%20unit-wise%20printed%20textbook%20with%20creative%20ways%20to%20teach%20the%20children.%20In%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENarmada%20Samala%2C%20a%20rural%20teacher%20fellow%20in%20a%20school%20in%20Khammam%20district%20of%20Telangana%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTeachers%20are%20trained%20to%20develop%20their%20skills%20so%20that%20they%20can%20train%20students%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20what%20makes%20the%20teaching%20method%20unique%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20have%20to%20teach%20students%20about%20prepositions%2C%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20start%20by%20teaching%20them%20the%20definition%20and%20what%20are%20the%20words%20of%20prepositions%20on%20board.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20a%20teacher%20hides%20any%20object%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%20and%20students%20are%20asked%20if%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98under%E2%80%99%20the%20table%20or%20is%20it%20%E2%80%98in%E2%80%99%20the%20bag.%20After%20the%20activities%2C%20we%20tell%20the%20students%20that%20the%20words%20they%20used%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98in%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98under%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98on%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98behind%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98beside%E2%80%99%2C%20are%20called%20prepositions.%20So%2C%20they%20easily%20understand%20the%20concept.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20teach%20other%20grammar%20concepts.%20This%20helps%20engage%20all%20the%20students%20and%20we%20see%20a%20great%20improvement%20in%20oral%20as%20well%20as%20writing%20skills%20of%20students.%20This%20kind%20of%20training%20is%20not%20happening%20anywhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20Rennis%20charges%20up%20to%20Rs%20700%20per%20student%20per%20year%20from%20low-cost%20private%20schools.%20For%20government%20schools%2C%20they%20do%20not%20charge%20any%20amount%20and%20manage%20expenses%20through%20CSR%20donations.%20But%20there%20have%20been%20times%20when%20he%20had%20to%20borrow%20from%20his%20friends%20to%20run%20the%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rennis%20and%20Imma%20started%20Ignis%20Careers%20in%202014.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-4-1691584816-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326824%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERennis%20and%20Imma%20started%20Ignis%20Careers%20in%202014.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202016%20after%20demonetisation%2C%20we%20were%20affected%20for%20two%20years%20as%20were%20our%20partners.%20We%20did%20not%20receive%20sufficient%20funds%20to%20run%20the%20startup.%20In%202017%2C%20I%20was%20so%20short%20on%20money%20that%20I%20had%20to%20pull%20my%20children%20out%20of%20school%20because%20I%20could%20not%20afford%20their%20fees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20we%20conducted%20a%20study%20and%20found%20that%2094%20percent%20of%20parents%20from%20various%20cities%20we%20are%20working%20in%20saw%20improvement%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20of%20the%20students.%20Our%20training%20methods%20make%20young%20people%20confident.%20These%20experiences%20give%20us%20hope.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20about%20the%20happiness%20on%20the%20faces%20of%20our%20students%20and%20the%20freshness%20we%20are%20able%20to%20bring%20into%20classrooms.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20someone%20who%20wants%20a%20strong%20purpose%20to%20live%2C%20and%20when%20you%20find%20the%20impact%2C%20you%20are%20motivated%20to%20do%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rennis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Rennis%20Joseph.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691646234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-3-1691584758.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theb