ing%20and%20animal%20abuse%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20also%20started%20sensitisation%20of%20police%20officers%20towards%20animal%20cruelty.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20conducting%20seminars%20in%202021%20and%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20nearly%202%2C000%20police%20offers.%20It%20is%20important%20because%20many%20officers%20in%20rural%20areas%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20laws%20against%20animal%20abuse%20and%20the%20correct%20measures%20to%20take%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%E2%80%99s%20inbox%20and%20phone%20are%20always%20buzzing%20with%20requests%20from%20people%20all%20around%20the%20city%20as%20well%20as%20the%20outskirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThree%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20found%20a%20cow%20that%20had%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20and%20injured%20its%20leg.%20It%20was%20in%20deep%20pain%20and%20needed%20immediate%20attention.%20I%20had%20seen%20many%20of%20Sai%E2%80%99s%20reels%20on%20Instagram%20and%20was%20aware%20of%20his%20work.%20So%20I%20called%20for%20his%20help%2C%20and%20he%20rescued%20the%20cow%20and%20took%20it%20to%20his%20sanctuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kathir%20Selvan%20who%20has%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20Sai%20ever%20since.%20He%20now%20informs%20Sai%20of%20any%20animal%20in%20distress%20that%20he%20happens%20to%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sai%20conducts%20sensitization%20seminars%20with%20the%20police%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691