.com%2F172628%2Ftelangana-police-hero-snake-rescue-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20rescues%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20gives%20them%20first%20aid%2C%20and%20leads%20awareness%20programmes.%20We%20work%20across%20Madurai%2C%20Pollachi%2C%20Coimbatore%20and%20Chennai%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20work%20that%20Vedhapriya%20does%20at%20WGWCT%20and%20other%20organisations%20is%20honorary.%20To%20support%20her%20family%2C%20she%20works%20as%20a%20pet%20stylist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20520px)%20100vw%2C%20520px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmonkey-1691584002.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vedhapriya%20loves%20animals%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmonkey-1691584002.jpeg%20520w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmonkey-1691584002-135x300.jpeg%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmonkey-1691584002-462x1024.jpeg%20462w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmonkey-1691584002-150x332.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326817%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVedhapriya%20has%20specialised%20in%20wildlife%20rescue.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20everyone%20understand%20that%20all%20creatures%20have%20equal%20rights.%20Do%20not%20hurt%20or%20kill%20any%20species%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20help%20Vedhapriya%20and%20the%20WGWCT%20with%20snake%20rescue%20equipment%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20her%20at%209940540921.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A169158746000