ity%20of%20pastoralists%2C%20camel%20herders%2C%20sheep%20goat%20rearers%2C%20and%20indigenous%20cow%20rearers.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20challenging%20geographies%20and%20extreme%20temperatures%2C%20these%20communities%20would%20travel%20eight%20months%20on%20foot%20covering%20800%20km%20of%20stretch%20with%20their%20herds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPastoralism%20has%20been%20enriching%20the%20desert%20soil%20all%20these%20years.%20Whatever%20organic%20greenery%20that%20we%20see%20in%20deserts%20is%20because%20of%20their%20movement.%20When%20the%20pastoralists%20are%20on%20the%20move%20with%20livestock%2C%20their%20droppings%20rejuvenate%20the%20pasture%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20sells%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20camel%20milk%20ghee%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20Cheshire%20cheese%2C%20and%20cold-pressed%20oils.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326698%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20sells%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80