99%20in%202013%2C%20and%20have%20converted%20over%20seven%20lakh%20glass%20bottles%20into%20pieces%20of%20home%20utility%20and%20decor%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20had%20sustainability%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20project%2C%20we%20also%20wanted%20to%20earn%20money%20so%20we%20could%20pay%20off%20the%20rag%20pickers%20and%20other%20employees.%20So%20we%20started%20to%20host%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274565%2Flibrarian-grows-vegetable-fruits-flowers-on-terrace-gardening-facebook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20Facebook%20campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E%20urging%20people%20to%20come%20join%20us%20with%20their%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20advertised%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20caught%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20%E2%80%94%20we%20asked%20them%20to%20come%20with%20their%20bottles%20and%20that%20we%20would%20convert%20the%20bottles%20into%20whatever%20piece%20they%20fancied.%20This%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20our%20business%2C%20and%20by%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20we%20started%20getting%20flooded%20with%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20products%20are%20priced%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%20300%20and%20Rs%201%2C600.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20did%20not%20have%20any%20formal%20training%20in%20working%20with%20glass%2C%20so%20they%20had%20their%20fair%20share%20of%20mistakes.%20%E2%80%9CGlass%20breaks%20very%20easily%20and%20we%20have%20to%20be%20quite%20careful%20with%20it.%20We%20used%20the%20internet%20and%20hired%20some%20glass%20artists%20to%20help%20us%20with%20the%20process.%20We%20have%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20hits%20and%20misses%2C%20but%20it%20is%20practice%20alone%20that%20has%20helped%20us%20come%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Madhuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Madhuri%20collects%20bottles%20from%20customers%20and%20ragpickers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326398%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20collect%20glass%20bottles%20and%20convert%20them%20into%20serving%20sets%2C%20platters%2C%20lamps%20etc%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Madhuri%20Balodi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20they%20focus%20on%20the%20finishing%20touches%20very%20carefully%20so%20the%20products%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20upcycled%2C%20but%20rather%20feel%20brand%20new!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20social%20media%20campaigns%20also%20resulted%20in%20something%20very%20sweet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20came%20to%20us%20with%20their%20bottles%2C%20many%20shared%20special%20stories%20behind%20each%20of%20them!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20people%20saying%20things%20like%20%E2%80%98I%20opened%20this%20bottle%20when%20my%20daughter%20was%20born%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98My%20best%20friend%20gifted%20me%20this%20bottle%2020%20years%20ago%E2%80%99.%20They%20come%20to%20us%20with%20requests%20to%20save%20the%20bottles%20and%20preserve%20them%20in%20a%20memorable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhuri%20and%20Amit%20share%20that%20such%20requests%20and%20stories%20make%20their%20jobs%20even%20more%20special%20and%20add%20an%20element%20of%20challenge%20to%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20from%20waste%20to%20wonder%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20the%20process%20of%20upcycling%20starts%2C%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20ways%20in%20which%20we%20collect%20bottles.%20First%2C%20through%20our%20BYOB%20(bring%20your%20own%20bottle)%20initiative%2C%20we%20transform%20the%20bottles%20that%20people%20bring%20to%20us%20into%20whatever%20they%20request%20them%20to%20be.%20Second%2C%20we%20collaborate%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300446%2Ffriends-help-ragpickers-in-kolkata-slum-launch-sustainable-children-fashion-brand-khudey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20with%20rag%20pickers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20collect%20and%20bring%20bottles%20to%20us%2C%20for%20which%20we%20pay%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20and%20Madhuri%20have%20a%20network%20of%20more%20than%20150%20ragpickers%20in%20and%20around%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20collected%20bottles%20are%20sanitised%2C%20and%20then%20a%20rough%20design%20is%20made.%20We%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20into%20what%20can%20be%20made%20out%20of%20these%20bottles.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20people%20to%20just%20view%20them%20as%20pieces%20of%20decor.%20We%20want%20to%20promote%20the%20reuse%20of%20products%2C%20so%20we%20make%20utility%20items%20like%20platters%20and%20bowls%20out%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Madhuri%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20firmly%20believes%20that%20upcycling%20is%20the%20way%20forward%20and%20wants%20more%20businesses%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuzrPPOhBpG%2F